items.name: name:privacy_statement_msg_1
items.zh:
AR测量”是利用增强现实技术，提供物体测量服务的软件。本应用使用过程中需要调用以下手机权限：使用摄像头、获取位置信息、读取存储卡数据、写入存储卡数据。为了给您提供更好的产品体验，需收集使用您的下列信息：需收集使用您的下列信息：

设备信息，包括唯一设备识别符，屏幕尺寸、操作系统、终端型号、系统区域；
操作行为数据，包括操作路径、操作结果、操作的内容数据；

上述数据只有您在应用中明示授权后才会上传 OPPO 服务器。您的上述数据将会保存至中华人民共和国境内服务器。 

如果您不同意我们采集上述信息，或不同意调用相关手机权限或功能，将可能导致本软件无法正常运行。您可以通过访问“设置”>“应用管理”>“AR测量”>“存储占用”>“清除数据”终止以上数据或信息的处理。

items.name: name:statement_outer_msg
items.zh:
Breeno 空间是一种全新的自然交互方式，记忆、学习、整合您散落在各处的信息，提供不同场景下的个性化服务。同时，根据您当前所处的生活场景，提供有价值的 Breeno 建议。为了实现前述目的，我们在向您提供服务时，可能需要收集或从独立的应用程序或功能中同步您提供的或您设备的相关信息（包括但不限于个人信息），例如：
1、为了识别当前所使用该功能的设备及进行设备安全控制，我们需要获得您的设备信息（如：IMEI）；
2、为了向您提供个性化的智能信息服务，您需要注册或登录 HeyTap 帐号，HeyTap 帐号可能会要求您提供个人信息,如手机号码、电子邮箱、帐号名称及密码等，您在注册 HeyTap 帐号时，需要另行同意《HeyTap 帐号隐私声明》。同时，我们需要获取您 HeyTap 帐号、昵称及头像，以便在 Breeno 相关设置项中显示；
3、为了向您提供“上下班通勤建议”的功能，我们需要获得您的位置信息；
4、为了向您提供“会议静音建议”的功能，我们需要获得您的会议类型的日程信息（此信息由数据服务平台在您授权同意后进行读取），以便在相应的时间提醒您将手机静音。
5、为了向您提供飞机、火车、电影、酒店、快递等服务，我们需要在您的设备本地分析您的短信信息，但我们仅将分析结果上传至服务器，以便更新最新的服务信息，及时向您呈现。如，我们会获得您的航班信息，并向您提供行程展示及查询服务；
6、为了优化产品功能，个性化您的用户体验，我们会根据大部分用户的使用习惯数据，优化我们的界面布局逻辑，使得软件界面布局更合理，我们需要获取您的操作行为数据，如产品功能使用统计数据。
我们将严格遵守前述载明的目的来使用您的个人信息，您的个人信息将仅用于收集时即已确定并且经过您同意的目的，如有除此之外的任何其他用途，我们都会提前征得您的同意。同时，我们将采取一切合理可行的有针对性的组织和技术措施，以保护您的个人信息，防止其遭到未经授权的访问、公开披露、使用、修改、损坏或丢失。例如，我们会使用加密技术确保数据传输、存储的安全性。
您知悉并理解，Breeno 空间中可能包含我们的合作伙伴提供的服务，在获取您的同意后，我们可能会向他们共享您提供的信息，以提供更好的客户服务和用户体验。如将您的位置信息分享给地图服务提供商，以便为您提供通勤服务。将您的航班信息分享给航班信息服务提供商，以便您查看您的航班状态。除本说明载明的情况外，未经您的同意，我们将不会向第三方披露您的个人信息，用于其各自的独立市场营销或商业用途。
如果您需要使用第三方服务提供商提供的服务，第三方可能会收集您的信息。我们无法控制第三方的隐私和数据保护政策，此类第三方不受到本协议的约束。您在向第三方提交个人数据之前，请阅读这些第三方的隐私保护政策。
在您停止使用 Breeno 空间的某些功能后，Breeno 空间将停止收集或同步您与这些功能有关的个人信息。
如果您不同意我们采集上述信息，您可以点击“不同意”关闭 Breeno 空间，但这将导致本软件无法正常运行，我们将无法为您提供服务。在您启用 Breeno 空间后，您可以通过访问“设置-应用管理-Breeno 空间-清除数据”来终止 Breeno 空间继续处理您的数据。
若您点击“同意”以启用 Breeno 空间功能，意味着您充分明确地了解上述的信息收集和使用行为（包括但不限于其范围、方式、目的与期限等）以及您所拥有的权利等事宜，并同意我们收集和使用您提供的和您的设备的相关信息。

items.en:
Breeno Space is a new, natural way of interaction to remember, learn, and integrate information you scattered everywhere to provide personalized services in different scenarios. It also can provide valuable Breeno Suggestions based on your current scenario. To this end, when we provide services to you, we may need to collect or synchronize from separate applications or functions information that you provide or information related to your device (including but not limited to personal information), such as:
1. To identify the device that is currently using this function and to monitor device security, we need to get your device information (such as the IMEI);
2. For us to provide you with smart personalized messaging services, you need to register or sign in with an OPPO ID. This may require you to provide personal information, such as a mobile number, e-mail, account name and password. When you register an OPPO ID, you are required to separately agree to the OPPO ID Privacy Statement. At the same time, we need to get your OPPO ID, display name, and profile photo to display in the relevant Breeno settings;
3. We need to get your location information to provide you with the "Commuting Suggestions";
4. To provide you with services such as flights, trains, movies, hotels and express deliveries, we need to analyze your SMS messages locally on your device, but we will only upload the analysis results to the server to update the latest service information and present it to you in time. For example, we will get your flight information to display your itinerary and offer you query services.
5. To optimize the product function and personalize your user experience, we optimize the layout logic of our interface based on the usage habit data of most users to make the layout of our software interface more reasonable. To do this, we need to get data about your operational behavior, such as product function usage statistics.
We will strictly abide by the purpose stated in the aforementioned when your personal information is used. Your personal information will only be used for the purposes that have been established at the time of collection with your consent. In the event that such information may be used for any other purposes, we will seek your prior consent before we proceed. Meanwhile, we will take all reasonable, feasible and pertinent organizational and technical measures to protect your personal information to prevent unauthorized access, public disclosure, use, modification, damage or loss. For example, we will use encryption technology to ensure security of data transmission and storage.
You shall acknowledge and understand that Breeno Space may include services provided by our partners, and that after obtaining your consent, we may share with them the information you provide to us so as to offer you better customer service and user experience. For example, we may share your location information with mapping service providers in order to provide you with commuting services. We may share your flight information with the flight information service provider so that you can check your flight status. Unless otherwise stated in this statement, we will not disclose your personal information to third parties without your prior consent for their respective independent marketing or commercial use.
If you need to use services provided by third-party service providers, the third parties may collect your information. We have no control over third-party privacy and data protection policies as such third parties are not bound by this Agreement. Before you submit personal data to third parties, please read their privacy protection policies.
Once you have stopped using certain functions of Breeno Space, it will stop collecting or syncing your personal information related to these functions.
If you do not agree to us collecting the above information, you can tap "Disagree" to close Breeno Space, however this will cause the app to run improperly, and we will be unable to provide you with the services. After you have turned on Breeno Space, you can stop Breeno Space from processing your data by accessing "Settings - App Management - Breeno Space - Clear Data".
If you tap "Agree" to enable the Breeno Space functions, it means that you fully understand the above-mentioned on information collection and use (including but not limited to its scope, method, purpose and timeline), and on matters such as your rights, and you agree that we can collect and use the information that you have provided and information related to your device.

您知悉并理解，Breeno 空间中可能包含我们的合作伙伴提供的服务，在获取您的同意后，我们可能会向他们共享您提供的信息，以提供更好的客户服务和用户体验。如将您的位置信息分享给地图服务提供商，以便为您提供通勤服务。将您的航班信息分享给航班信息服务提供商，以便您查看您的航班状态。除本说明载明的情况外，未经您的同意，我们将不会向第三方披露您的个人信息，用于其各自的独立市场营销或商业用途。

在您停止使用 Breeno 空间的某些功能后，Breeno 空间将停止收集或同步您与这些功能有关的个人信息。
如果您不同意我们采集上述信息，您可以点击“不同意”关闭 Breeno 空间，但这将导致本软件无法正常运行，我们将无法为您提供服务。在您启用 Breeno 空间后，您可以通过访问“设置-应用管理-Breeno 空间-清除数据”来终止 Breeno 空间继续处理您的数据。

items.name: name:private_policy_text_68
items.zh: ColorOS不会在明知对方为无行为能力人的情况下收集其个人信息，也不会向任何第三方透露其个人信息，监护人有权拒绝ColorOS及其关联公司进一步收集被监护人的个人信息，或要求ColorOS及其关联公司删除该被监护人个人信息。如果我们发现我们收集了无行为能力人的个人信息，我们将采取措施尽快地删除此等信息。
items.en: ColorOS will not knowingly collect personal information of individuals who do not have the capacity to act on their own, and will not disclose such personal information to any third parties. The guardian shall have the right to deny any further collection by ColorOS and its associated companies of the personal information of the person under guardianship, or to request ColorOS and its associated companies to delete the personal information of the person under guardianship. If we discover we have collected the personal information of a person without the capacity to act, we will take measures to delete such information as soon as possible.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_20
items.zh: ColorOS将严格遵守本隐私政策及其更新所载明的内容来使用您的个人信息。您的个人信息将仅用于收集时即已确定并且经过您同意的目的，如有除此之外的任何其他用途，我们都会提前征得您的同意。
items.en: ColorOS will strictly abide by the requirements stated in this Privacy Policy and its updates when using your personal information. Your personal information will only be used for the purposes that have been established and consented to by you at the time of collection. We will seek your prior consent in the event of use for any other purposes.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_35

items.name: name:oppo_protocol_22
items.zh: OPPO可能会收集某些信息进行统计与分析，这类信息可包括您的设备名称、设备版本、设备识别号码 (IMEI、SN)、设备的粗略地理位置信息 (例如设备所在的网络位置编码)、运营商网络ID(PLMN)、应用使用情况、您访问互联网的IP地址。OPPO收集并处理这类信息的目的是:提供您最佳的人性化用户体验、提供个性化内容、改善我们的产品、分析我们的运营效率、统计市场占有率、改善网络和服务的安全性，以及为您启用相应的售后保障服务。
items.en: OPPO may collect certain information for statistics and analysis. Such information may include your device name, device version, device identification number (IMEI, SN), approximate geographic location of the device (e.g., code of network location where the device is used), carrier network ID (PLMN), app usage, and the IP address that you use to access the Internet. OPPO collects and processes such information so that we can provide you with the best customized user experience and personalized contents, improve our products, analyze our operational efficiency, calculate market share, make networks and services more secure, and provide you with the relevant after-sales services.

items.name: name:oppo_protocol_20
items.zh: OPPO可能收集您终端产品的系统和应用程序信息，这是为了及时通知您有可用的ColorOS系统和应用程序更新。因为此目的收集的信息包括设备名称、系统和应用程序版本、操作系统和浏览器版本、地区和语言设置、设备识别信息 (IMEI、ESN、MEID、SN)、运营商网络编码等。OPPO对以上信息的处理仅限于通知您有ColorOS系统版本的升级和应用程序的更新。
items.en: OPPO may collect information about the system and applications of your devices in order to promptly notify you of available updates for the ColorOS system and applications. The information collected for this purpose includes device name, system and application version, OS and browser version, region and language settings, device identification information (IMEI, ESN, MEID, SN), and carrier network code among others. OPPO processes the above information solely for the purpose of notifying you of available ColorOS system upgrades and app updates.

items.name: name:First_Load_Detail

items.name: 日，阿姆斯特朗与奥尔德林成为了首次踏上月球的人类。"
items.application: Apollo 11 was the fifth crewed mission of NASA's Apollo program, and the first spaceflight to land humans on the Moon. The mission duration was 8 days, 13 hours, 18 minutes, and 35 seconds. The command module orbited the Moon 30 times, and the time astronauts spent on the lunar surface was 21 hours, 36 minutes, and 20 seconds. On July 20, 1969, astronauts Neil Armstrong and Buzz Aldrin become the first humans to walk on the Moon.

items.name: name:guard_about_des_7

items.name: name:assisted_dialing_summary

items.name: name:assisted_dialing_summary
items.zh: 当您不在所选择的默认国家/地区时，漫游拨号助理将在拨打已有联系人电话时自动为您加拨所选国家/地区代码。
items.en: When you call a contact while outside your specified country/region, the calling code of the country/region will be automatically added for you.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_15
items.zh: 当您创建ColorOS账户、下载及更新ColorOS软件、参加在线调查或者参加其他与ColorOS的互动时，我们会要求您提供个人信息，包括但不限于您的姓名、电话号码、电子邮件地址、邮寄地址等。
items.en: When you create a ColorOS account, download and update ColorOS software, participate in online surveys or in other interactions with ColorOS, we will request you to provide personal information, including but not limited to your name, telephone number, email address and mailing address.

items.name: name:oppo_protocol_24
items.zh: 当您的设备或应用程序发生异常情况，且您��择将相关信息发送给OPPO，让OPPO或其合作方提供故障分析服务时，OPPO可能会收集相关信息，包括设备型号、应用程序的名称和版本、设备识别号码、错误日志等。
items.en: If your device or app shows any abnormalities and you choose to send relevant information to OPPO for a fault analysis by OPPO or its partners, OPPO may collect relevant information, including the device model, name and version of the app, device identification number and error log.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_16
items.zh: 当您购买ColorOS产品和服务时，我们会收集有关个人信息，包括但不限于：交货详情、银行帐号、信用卡详情、账单地址、信用核查以及其他财务信息、联系及交流的记录等。
items.en: When you purchase ColorOS products and services, we will collect relevant personal information, including but not limited to details of delivery, bank account, credit card details, billing address, credit check and other financial information, contact and transaction records.

items.name: name:wifi_display_wfd_off_hdmi_on

items.name: name:wifi_display_wfd_off_bt_on

items.name: name:wifi_display_bt_hdmi_off_wfd_on

items.name: name:headset_guide_content
items.zh:
当您佩戴 O-Free 并使用语音翻译对话时，可选择进入随行翻译模式。您可单击耳机说中文，对方按住手机上的按钮说英文，并分别从耳机和手机听取翻译结果。双语交流更顺畅。
如果您长时间没有进行操作，会自动退出随行翻译模式。
items.en:
When wearing O-Free and using voice translation, choose Headset Translation Mode. Tap the headset and speak Chinese, while the other person holds down the button to speak English. This way, you can listen to the translation from the headset and phone, making bilingual communication smoother.
It will automatically exit Headset Translation Mode when inactive.

items.name: name:headset_guide_content
items.zh:
当您佩戴 O-Free 并使用语音翻译对话时，可选择进入随行翻译模式。您可双击耳机说中文，对方按住手机上的按钮说英文，并分别从耳机和手机听取翻译结果。双语交流更顺畅。
如果您长时间没有进行操作，会自动退出随行翻译模式。
items.en:
When wearing O-Free and using voice translation, choose Headset Translation Mode. Tap the headset and speak Chinese, while the other person holds down the button to speak English. This way, you can listen to the translation from the headset and phone, making bilingual communication smoother.
It will automatically exit Headset Translation Mode when inactive.

items.name: name:headset_guide_content
items.zh:
当您佩戴 OPPO O-Free 并使用语音翻译对话时，可选择进入随行翻译模式。您可双击耳机说中文，对方按住手机上的按钮说英文，并分别从耳机和手机听取翻译结果。双语交流更顺畅。
如果您长时间没有进行操作，会自动退出随行翻译模式。
items.en:
When wearing OPPO O-Free and using voice translation, choose Headset Translation Mode. Tap the headset and speak Chinese, while the other person holds down the button to speak English. This way, you can listen to the translation from the headset and phone, making bilingual communication smoother.
It will automatically exit Headset Translation Mode when inactive.

items.name: name:headset_guide_content_oswing
items.zh: 当您佩戴耳机并使用语音翻译对话时，可选择进入随行翻译模式。您可双击多功能按键说中文，对方按住手机上的按钮说英文，并分别从手机和耳机听取翻译结果。双语交流更顺畅。
items.en: When wearing OPPO O-Free and using voice translation, choose Headset Translation Mode. Tap the headset and speak Chinese, while the other person holds down the button to speak English. This way, you can listen to the translation from the headset and phone, making bilingual communication smoother.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_17
items.zh: 当您使用ColorOS产品与家人和朋友分享您的内容、发送信息和产品或者在OPPO论坛上邀请其他人时，ColorOS会收集您提供的与上述人士有关的个人信息，如姓名、邮寄地址、电子邮件地址及电话号码等。
items.en: When you use a ColorOS product to share your content with your family and friends, send messages and products, or invite other people on the OPPO forum, ColorOS will collect the personal information that you provide for the above-mentioned instances such as their names, mailing addresses, email addresses and telephone numbers.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_18
items.zh: 当您首次使用并激活ColorOS支持的移动设备时，您的移动用户识别信息、移动设备唯一识别码以及您设备的大概地理位置信息将被发送给ColorOS。上述信息的收集也可能适用于您更新系统或软件、恢复出厂设置等情况。
items.en: When you use and activate for the first time the mobile device supported by ColorOS, your mobile user identification information, the unique identification code for your mobile device as well as information of the approximate geographic location of your device will be sent to ColorOS. Collection of the above information may be used during system or software updates and factory settings restoration among others.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_31
items.zh: 当您下载ColorOS软件及其更新、在ColorOS在线零售店注册、参加在线调查或者参加其他与ColorOS的互动时，我们会收集您诸如职业、语言、邮编、区号以及使用ColorOS产品所在的时区等信息。
items.en: When you are downloading the ColorOS software and updates, registering on a ColorOS online retail store, participating in an online survey or engaging in other interactions with ColorOS, we will collect information such as your profession, language, postcode, area code and the time zone where the ColorOS product is used.

items.name: name:oppo_protocol_28
items.zh: 当您要求使用某些以地理位置信息为基础的服务时，例如，当您根据特定地理位置搜索，OPPO可能会收集、使用及处理您设备的精准或粗略地理位置数据，以便OPPO向您提供上述服务，收集的信息可包括您设备IMEI和型号，以及您设备的实时地理位置信息 (包括全球定位系统信息「GPS」、WLAN 或运营商网络编码)。您可以通过GPS设置，开启或关闭GPS信息，但是根据运营商的政策，您可能无权控制WLAN和选择移动运营商网络。OPPO采用匿名方式收集地理位置信息，以提供并改善以位置为基础的产品和服务。
items.en: When you request certain location-based services, such as making searches based on specific geographic locations, OPPO may collect, use, and process data about the precise or approximate geographic location of your device so as to provide you with the above services. The information collected may include the IMEI number and model of your device, as well as the real-time geographic location of the device (including GPS information, Wi-Fi or carrier network code). You can control the collection of GPS information by turning on or off the GPS setting. However, depending on the carrier's policy, you may not have control over Wi-Fi or be able to choose the carrier network. The geographic location information OPPO collects is made anonymous, and is used to provide and improve location-based products and services.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_75
items.zh: 当您在使用ColorOS云同步找回手机服务时，会上传的个人信息中也包括位置信息。一旦您启用ColorOS云同步服务，您的个人内容将被自动发送给服务器并由服务器存储，之后您就可访问该等信息或以无线方式将信息推送至您的其他启用ColorOS云同步服务功能的装置。
items.en: When you are using ColorOS cloud synchronization to find mobile phone services, the personal information to be uploaded also includes information of location. Once you have launched the ColorOS cloud synchronization service, your personal contents will be automatically sent to the server and stored there. Thereafter you will be able to access such information or push such information through wireless connection to your other devices that has the ColorOS cloud synchronization service enabled.

items.name: name:color_keybord_view_detail_message
items.zh: 当您在输入密码等敏感信息时，系统会自动切换为 OPPO 安全键盘，OPPO 安全键盘不会记录您的输入内容，不联网、不联想，保障您的输入内容不被泄露。
items.en: When you enter sensitive information such as a password, your keyboard will be automatically switched to OPPO Secure Keyboard. For security purposes, the Keyboard will not record your input, connect to Internet, or give suggestions.

items.name: name:rescreening
items.zh: 第2次筛查过程(复筛)：即出生42天内的婴儿初筛没“通过”；或初筛“可疑”；甚至初筛已经“通过”，但属于听力损失高危儿如重症监护病房患儿，需要进行听力复筛。
items.en: A rescreening is performed on infants less than 42 days old who: failed the initial screening; were suspected in the initial screening to have hearing loss; passed the initial screening but are at high risk of hearing loss, such as those in intensive care.

items.name: name:pure_background_detail_on
items.zh: 第三方应用转入后台冻结将不会耗费流量、电量及CPU，可有效防止恶意软件后台偷跑流量及后台推送垃圾信息。建议QQ、微信等聊天应用不要转入后台冻结，会造成无法及时收到聊天消息。
items.en: Moving third-party apps into the background and freezing them will stop their data usage, and power & CPU consumption, which can effectively prevent malware from sending out spam messages and using data without your knowledge. We recommend leaving chat apps such as Facebook, Twitter unsuspended, otherwise you may not receive chat messages in a timely manner.

items.name: name:pure_background_detail_on

items.en: Apps in the background will not be able to consume network traffic, power and CPU when data saving is turned on.

items.name: name:pure_background_detail_on
items.zh: 第三方应用转入后台将不会耗费流量、电量及CPU，可有效防止恶意软件后台偷跑流量及后台推送垃圾信息。建议QQ、微信等聊天应用不要转入后台冻结，会造成无法及时收到聊天消息。
items.en: Transferring third-party apps to the background will not consume data, battery or CPU and can effectively prevent malicious software from running up data bills and sending spam information in the background. You are recommended not to freeze chat applications such as Facebook and Twitter in the background. Otherwise, messages may be delayed.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_62
items.zh: 对我们来说，您的信息的安全非常重要。因此，我们将不断努力保障您的个人信息安全，并实施存储和传输全程安全加密等保障手段，以免您的信息在未经授权的情况下被访问、使用或披露。同时某些加密数据的具体内容，除了用户自己，其他人都无权访问。
items.en: Your information security is very important to us. Therefore, we will keep working hard to ensure the security of your personal information, and implement security measures including the security encryption of the whole process from storage to transmission, to prevent your information from being accessed, used or disclosed without authorization. At the same time, the specific contents of certain encrypted data will be made available only for the user and not anyone else.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_66
items.zh: 对无/限制行为能力人个人信息的收集和使用

items.name: name:direct_instructions_description_clip
items.zh: 对应用中的文本进行复制操作后，将提供信息推送和选词编辑功能。已支持地址、美食、影视、快递、航班、车次和淘口令等信息服务。
items.en: Pushing of information, words selection and editing functions will be provided after copying text in the app. Supported information services include addresses, fine dining, movies and TV programs, couriers, flights, train info, and Taobao passphrases.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_49
items.zh: 对于那些无端重复、需要过多技术投入、对他人隐私权造成风险或者非常不切实际的请求，我们可能予以拒绝。
items.en: We may deny requests which are repeated for no reason, which require too much technical investment, which cause risks to other's privacy rights, or which are very impracticable.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_7
items.zh: 对于您授权我们收集的生物识别信息、健康信息等个人敏感信息，我们的广告平台无法访问，也不会将此类信息用于广告用途或与第三方合作伙伴共享。如果您的个人敏感信息将被我们用于此类目的，我们会征得您的单独明示授权。
items.en: Sensitive personal information that you have authorized us to collect, such as biometric and health information, is not accessible on our advertising platform, and will not be used for advertising purposes or shared with any third-party partner. We will obtain your explicit consent if sensitive personal information will be used for such purposes.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_33

items.name: name:oppo_protocol_43
items.zh: 根据国家法律法规变化及业务运营需要，OPPO有权对本协议不时地修改，并代替原来的协议。用户可随时登陆查阅最新协议；用户有义务不时关注并阅读最新版的协议及网站公告。如用户不同意更新后的协议，应立即停止接受本服务；如用户继续使用的，即视为同意更新后的协议。
items.en: In response to changes in national laws and regulations and its own business operations, OPPO has the right to modify this Agreement from time to time to replace the previous version. Users can sign in anytime to check the latest agreement, and users are obliged to check and read the latest version of this Agreement and website notices from time to time. If the user does not accept the revised agreement, the user shall stop using this Service. In the event that the user continues to use this Service after the Agreement is updated, the user shall be deemed to have accepted the updated agreement.

items.name: name:envelope_settings_warnings
items.zh:
关于“红包助手”

1.红包助手暂支持微信红包的提醒，后续将支持更多应用；
2.使用红包助手需要保证微信通知开启，可在“设置-通知与状态栏-通知管理-微信”中开启；
3.如果每次红包抢的太快，可能会被红包平台禁用红包功能。
items.en:
About "Red Packet Assistant"

1. Red Packet Assistant currently supports WeChat red packet alerts, and will support more apps later.
2. WeChat Notification is required to be enabled for Red Packet Assistant. You may enable it in "Settings-Notification & Status Bar-Notification Management-WeChat".
3. If a red packet is snatched too fast every time, it may be banned by the red packet platform.

items.name: name:envelope_settings_warnings
items.zh:
关于“红包助手”
1.红包助手暂支持微信红包的提醒，后续将支持更多应用；
2.使用红包助手需要保证微信通知开启，可在“设置-通知与状态栏-通知管理-微信”中开启；
3.如果每次红包抢的太快，可能会被红包平台禁用红包功能。
items.en:
About "Red Packet Assistant"
1. Red Packet Assistant supports reminders for WeChat red packets, and will support similar functions for other apps later.
2. Notifications need to be turned on for WeChat. Go to "Settings - Notification & Status Bar - Notifications - WeChat" to turn on.
3. If a user grabs red packets too fast every time, they may be banned by platform where the red packets are being distributed.

items.name: name:oppo_sa_setting_foot_description_wx
items.zh:
关于“快捷应用”：
1. 大部分游戏以及视频应用横屏时，支持以浮窗形式调出Messenger、WhatsApp等进行信息的浏览及基本功能操作。
2. 以浮窗形式启动的应用需要应用自身支持，可能存在部分功能异常，回到全屏下使用即可。
items.en:
About "Quick Apps":
1. When in landscape mode, most games and video apps allow you to open apps such as Messenger and WhatsApp in a floating window for message browsing and other basic functions.
2. The app itself needs to support the floating window feature for it to work. If some of its functions are not working properly, use the app in full-screen mode.

1. When in landscape mode, most games and video apps allow you to call and run apps such as WeChat, Messenger, and WhatsApp in a floating window for message browsing and other basic functions.
2. The app itself needs to support the floating window feature for it to work. If some of its functions are not working properly, use the app in full-screen mode.

items.name: name:paragraph_title_1783_26
items.zh: 国际上网：一键上网，轻松游全球

items.name: name:text_roaming_stop

items.name: name:first_tip
items.zh: 国际上网提供免实体 SIM 卡，低资费，一键境外上网服务。
items.en: ORoaming provides SIM-free, low-rate, overseas Internet access with a single tap.

items.name: name:text_about_text
items.zh: 国际上网为出境旅游人士提供平台来购买境外当地运营商的网络套餐。购买套餐后，无需再购买实体 SIM 卡即可在出境旅游期间享受到便捷的数据网络服务。
items.en: ORoaming provides international travelers with a platform to purchase cellular data packages from local carriers in destination countries. After purchasing a package, you do not need to buy a real SIM card in order to enjoy a convenient cellular data network service when you are traveling abroad.

items.name: name:text_about_text
items.zh: 国际上网为用户提供全球范围内多个地区的当地运营商流量套餐。购买套餐后，无需再购买实体 SIM 卡即可便捷上网。
items.en: ORoaming provides data packages from local carriers in many locations worldwide. Purchasing a data package lets you access the Internet without a SIM card.

items.name: name:text_about_text
items.zh: 国际上网为用户提供全球范围内多个地区的当地运营商流量套餐。购买套餐后，无需再购买实体 SIM 卡即可在便捷上网。
items.en: ORoaming provides data packages of local carriers across many places worldwide. Purchasing a data package lets you access the Internet without a SIM card.

items.name: name:tips_permission_phone

items.name: name:Curiosity_Detail
items.zh: 好奇号是一辆美国宇航局火星科学实验室辖下的火星探测器，主要为了探索火星的盖尔撞击坑。其任务包括：火星气候及地质，探测盖尔撞击坑内的环境是否曾经能够支持生命，探测火星上的水，及研究日后人类探索的可行性，属于美国宇航局火星科学实验室计划的一部分。
items.en: Curiosity is a rover designed to explore the crater Gale on Mars as part of NASA's Mars Science Laboratory mission. The rover's goals include an investigation of the Martian climate and geology; assessment of whether the selected field site inside Gale has ever offered environmental conditions favorable for microbial life, including investigation of the role of water; and planetary habitability studies in preparation for human exploration.

items.name: name:oppo_sa_setting_description

items.name: name:fingerprint_recognition_statement_line2
items.zh: 敬请注意：您主动提供的指纹信息将仅存储在您手机的本地存储器中，并仅用于实现指纹解锁或支付的目的。未经您的事先明示同意，我们不会将指纹信息上传至公司服务器，从而也不具有将这些信息向任何其他第三方披露或用于其他任何用途的可能性。
items.en: Attention: The fingerprint information you choose to provide is only stored locally on your mobile phone, and is only used for the purpose of unlocking with fingerprint. Without your explicit prior consent, we will not upload your fingerprint information to the company's corporate servers and therefore do not have the possibility of disclosing such information to any third party or use them for any other purpose.

items.name: name:face_recognition_statement_line2
items.zh: 敬请注意：您主动选择提供的面容特征信息将仅存储在您手机的本地存储器中，并仅用于实现面部识别的目的。我们不会将面部特征信息上传至公司服务器，从而也不具有将这些信息向任何其他第三方披露或用于其他任何用途的可能性。
items.en: Attention: Information of the facial features you choose to provide is only stored locally on your mobile phone, and is only used for face recognition purpose. We do not upload facial features to the company's corporate servers and therefore do not have the possibility of disclosing such information to any third party or use them for any other purpose.

items.name: name:heart_rate_rest_intro
items.zh:
静息心率，又称为安静心率，是指在清醒、不活动的安静状态下，每分钟心跳的次数。

静息心率一般在早上起床的时候测得。经常运动的人，静息心率相比普通人要低一些。
items.en:
Your resting heart rate is the number of times your heart beats per minute while at rest.

It is best measured first thing in the morning when you wake up naturally. People who exercise more often tend to have lower resting heart rates.

items.name: name:health_heart_rate_rest_description
items.zh: 静息心率，又称为安静心率，是指在清醒、不活动的安静状态下，每分钟心跳的次数。一般在清晨醒来时测得的结果更为准确。
items.en: Your resting heart rate is the number of times your heart beats per minute while at rest. It is best measured first thing in the morning when you wake up naturally.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_10
items.zh: 具体方法是通过“设置-安全-设备标识与广告”开启“限制广告追踪”，以限制基于设备标识进行推荐的个性化广告。在您开启“限制广告跟踪”后，该状态将会同步至我们的广告平台及与我们合作的第三方合作伙伴，我们将尊重您的选择，限制向您发送个性化广告。
items.en: You can turn on Limit Ad Tracking in "Settings - Security - Device ID & Ads". After you turn this feature on, this setting will be synced to our advertising platform and our third-party partners. We will respect your choice and will no longer push device ID-based ads to you.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_10
items.zh: 具体方法是通过“设置-其他设置-设备与隐私-设备标识与广告”开启“限制广告追踪”，以限制基于设备标识进行推荐的个性化广告。在您开启“限制广告跟踪”后，该状态将会同步至我们的广告平台及与我们合作的第三方合作伙伴，我们将尊重您的选择，限制向您发送个性化广告。
items.en: You can turn on Limit Ad Tracking in "Settings - Additional Settings - Device and Privacy - Device ID and Ads", in order to restrict targeted advertising based on your device ID. After you have turned on Limit Ad Tracking, the status will be synced to our advertising platform and our third-party partners. We will respect your choice and restrict the delivery of targeted advertising to you.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_10

items.en: Go to "Settings - Additional Settings - Get Recommendations" and turn off the content recommendation feature. Ads will no longer be pushed to you based on your device ID. After you turn off the feature, your setting will be synchronized to our advertising platform and our third-party partners. We will respect your choice and will no longer push ads to you.

items.name: name:daily_distance_height_explain
items.zh:
距离根据你每天行走的步数和运动里程，结合身高体重等指标精确计算得出。
爬楼由智能算法进行精确统计。
items.en:
Distance is calculated based on both the number of steps you take and the distance generated from your workouts in a day, in combination with other physical indicators like your weight and height.
The number of floors you climb is calculated using algorithms.

4. The battery icon will be displayed in blue.

items.name: name:wlan_display_info_phone_tip_3
items.zh: 开启“手机投屏”开关后，搜索连接大屏设备。
items.en: Find the display in the device list and connect your phone to it.

items.name: name:runtime_permission_call_log
items.en: Turn On the Call Logs Permission

items.name: name:gui_location_dialog_title
items.en: Turn On the Location Info Permission

items.name: name:runtime_permission_location
items.en: Turn On the Location Info Permission

items.name: name:oppo_navigation_bar_hide_summary
items.zh: 开启“指纹传感器手势”后可选择
items.en: Selectable after turning on "Fingerprint Sensor Palm"

items.name: name:screen_pinning_description_gesture_new
items.zh: 开启<xliff:g id="ID_1">%1$s</xliff:g>后，固定屏幕功能将无法使用。
items.en: Screen Pinning is unavailable if <xliff:g id="NAME">%1$s</xliff:g> is turned on.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_tip_info
items.zh: 开启保护后，系统将提供空的%1$s代替真实%2$s，避免个人信息泄露。
items.en: When turned on, real %1$s information will be replaced with empty %2$s information to avoid personal information leakage.

items.name: name:oppo_fingerprint_face_combination_unlock_disable_tip
items.zh: 开启此功能需启用人脸和指纹解锁。
items.en: To turn on this function, you need to enable facial and fingerprint unlock.

items.name: name:toast_storage_content
items.zh: 开启存储权限以获取更新服务
items.en: Turn on the Storage permission to get content updates

items.name: name:navigation_talkback_warnning_dialog_title_gesture_side
items.zh: 开启读屏服务时，不允许开启两侧滑动手势导航。
items.en: Navigation by swipe gestures from both sides is not allowed when the Talkback service is on.

items.name: name:navigation_talkback_warnning_dialog_title
items.zh: 开启读屏服务时，不允许开启上滑手势导航。
items.en: Swipe-up Gesture Navigation Is Not Allowed When the Talkback Service Is On.

items.name: name:permission_title_open_wifi_in_airplane_mode_confirm_summary
items.zh: 开启飞行模式时，打开 WLAN 网络提醒
items.en: Turn On Wi-Fi Network Reminder when in Airplane Mode

items.name: name:curved_display_switch_dialog_message
items.zh: 开启该功能将关闭“来锁屏通知时点亮屏幕”。
items.en: If this is enabled, "Turn On Screen for Notifications" will be disabled.

items.name: name:oppo_curved_screen_settings_notify_open_split_dialog
items.zh: 开启该功能需先开启“应用分屏”，要开启吗?
items.en: "Split Screen" must be activated before enabling this feature. Activate now?

items.name: name:broadcast_introduce
items.zh: 开启后，“Breeno语音”将使用声音回复你。
items.en: Breeno Voice will speak back to you.

items.name: name:mute_tips
items.zh: 开启后，不影响闹钟及备忘事件提醒。
items.en: Alarms and Notes reminders will not be silenced.

items.name: name:dual_clock_tips
items.zh: 开启后，当您不在常驻城市时，锁屏或时钟桌面插件将显示两个城市的的时间。
items.en: When turned on, both the time of your city of residence and current city will be displayed on the Lock Screen or Home Screen clock widget whenever you are not in your city of residence.

items.name: name:dual_clock_tips
items.zh: 开启后，当您不在常驻城市时，锁屏或时钟桌面插件将显示两个城市的时间。
items.en: When turned on, both the time of your city of residence and current city will be displayed on the Lock Screen or Home Screen Clock Widget whenever you are not in your city of residence.

items.name: name:dual_clock_screenlock_tips
items.zh: 开启后，当您不在常驻城市时，锁屏将显示两个城市的时间。
items.en: When the widget is turned on, the times of both your city of residence and current city will be displayed on the Lock Screen whenever you are not in your city of residence.

items.name: name:dual_clock_tips
items.zh: 开启后，当您不在常驻地时，锁屏或时钟桌面插件将显示两个地区的时间。
items.en: When turned on, both the time of your residence and current city will be displayed on the Lock Screen or Home Screen Clock Widget whenever you are not in your city of residence.

items.name: name:relax_open_background_tip
items.zh: 开启后，呼吸、音乐、环境音将会继续在后台播放
items.en: Sounds in the Music, Ambient Sounds, and Breathing tabs will play normally in the background.

items.name: name:wlan_share_summary_new
items.zh: 开启后，将共享你的 WLAN 网络，可能会消耗更多电量，无设备连接 10 分钟后将自动关闭。
items.en: Turn on Wi-Fi tethering to share your Wi-Fi connection. This may consume more power. It automatically turns off when no device is connected for 10 minutes.

items.name: name:wlan_share_summary
items.zh: 开启后，将共享您的 WLAN 网络，可能会消耗更多电量，无设备连接 10 分钟后将自动关闭。
items.en: When this is on, your Wi-Fi network will be shared and more power may be consumed. It will automatically turn off if there is no device connected for more than 10 minutes.

items.name: name:use_dialog_positive_message
items.zh: 开启后，将会改变当前设定的主题，是否继续开启？
items.en: If turned on, the current theme will be changed. Turn it on?

items.name: name:wireless_reverse_charging_introduction
items.zh: 开启后，将支持的设备（若带有保护套，请取下）放于手机背面如上位置，即可开始充电。
items.en: To start charging a supported device, turn on Reverse Wireless Charging and place the device (protective case removed) on the back of your phone.

items.name: name:code_setting_switch_desc
items.zh: 开启后，可保存和自动填充应用的帐号和密码。
items.en: Automatically store your account passwords for autofill.

items.name: name:settings_dc_backlight_mode_tip
items.zh: 开启后，可降低屏幕低光频闪，缓解视疲劳，但部分场景显示效果可能受影响。
items.en: Reduces flickering at low light to alleviate visual fatigue when turned on, but some display effects may be affected.

items.name: name:oppo_ktv_loopback_switch_summer
items.zh: 开启后，可通过耳机在K歌过程中实时感受现场效果，同时请关闭K歌应用自带的耳机返听功能避免出现声音冲突。
items.en: Enjoy a live karaoke experience in real-time through your headphones. Turn off the in-ear monitoring function in the karaoke app to avoid sound issues.

items.name: name:wakeup_by_speech_introduce
items.zh: 开启后，可以使用唤醒词唤醒“Breeno语音”。
items.en: Use wakeup words to wake up Breeno Voice.

items.name: name:settings_watch_auto_measure_heart_rate_des
items.zh: 开启后，佩戴手表时，将全天自动测量你的心率，可能会加快电量消耗。
items.en: Measure your heart rate throughout the day when wearing your watch. This will increase power consumption.

items.name: name:settings_watch_sedentary_remind_description
items.zh: 开启后，佩戴手表时，在09:00-21:00时间段内，超过1小时未活动时会提醒你。
items.en: You will receive a reminder if you are wearing the watch and no active movement is detected within a 1-hour period from 09:00 to 21:00.

items.name: name:full_screen_simple_banner_summary
items.zh: 开启后，全屏时（例如看视频，玩游戏）会显示简化的横幅通知，减少通知对屏幕的遮挡。
items.en: Once turned on, Banner Notifications are displayed in full screen mode, such as when you are watching videos or playing games. This minimizes unwanted use of the screen.

items.name: name:zen_mode_media_summary
items.zh: 开启后，若增加媒体音量，则开关自动关闭。
items.en: Even though this is turned on, this switch will be automatically turned off if you increase the media volume.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_category_des_other
items.zh: 开启后，三方应用将读取到粗略位置，避免真实位置泄露
items.en: When turned on, only general location info will be read by third-party apps to avoid the leakage of real location info

items.name: name:privacy_protect_category_des_main
items.zh: 开启后，三方应用将读取到虚拟信息，避免个人信息泄露
items.en: When turned on, only virtual info will be read by third-party apps to avoid the leakage of personal information

items.name: name:settings_file_delete_protection_summary
items.zh: 开启后，三方应用删除相册的相机、屏幕截图、微信、QQ图集下的文件时通知提醒。
items.en: You will be alerted if a third-party app tries to delete images from the Camera, Screenshots, WeChat, or QQ albums.

items.name: name:settings_watch_auto_pause_des
items.zh: 开启后，使用手表进行运动（跑步、健走、骑行），检测到你停止移动时，手表将自动暂停记录，恢复移动后将自动继续。
items.en: When using your watch for exercise (running, walking, cycling), data recording will automatically pause when you are resting. Once you start moving again, data recording will resume.

items.name: name:settings_watch_high_rate_notification_description
items.zh: 开启后，使用手表运动，检测到你心率超过设置时，手表将通知你。
items.en: The watch will send you a reminder when your heart rate exceeds the set value.

items.name: name:privacy_deep_protect_app_summary
items.zh: 开启后，使用应用时将需要验证应用加密密码。
items.en: When this is on, you'll need to verify the app encryption passcode before using an app.

items.name: name:settings_watch_quiet_rate_notification_description
items.zh: 开启后，手表检测到你在非运动状态心率持续超过设置数值十分钟时，手表将通知你。
items.en: The watch will send you an alert when your resting heart rate remains above the set value for 10 minutes.

items.name: name:settings_sync_notification_description
items.zh: 开启后，手表将接收手机应用的消息通知。你正在使用手机时，手表会停止接收手机通知。
items.en: Receive messages and notifications from apps installed on your mobile phone. The watch will temporarily stop receiving these notifications whenever you use your phone.

items.name: name:turn_on_hint
items.zh: 开启后，调整应用页面为暗色效果。若应用自身已有暗色模式，可将其关闭。
items.en: Turn on the switch to set an app to Dark Mode. If an app has its own dark mode, you can turn its switch off.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_all_open_context_with_suggest
items.zh:
开启后，系统将提供空的%1$s代替真实%2$s，避免个人信息泄露。
注意：部分应用可能无法正常使用，建议关闭的应用将不会开启。
items.en:
When turned on, the system will provide empty %1$s instead of real %2$s to avoid personal information leakage.
Note: Some apps may not work properly, and apps that are recommended to be turned off will not be turned on.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_all_open_context
items.zh:
开启后，系统将提供空的%1$s代替真实%2$s，避免个人信息泄露。
注意：部分应用可能无法正常使用。
items.en:
When turned on, real %1$s information will be replaced with empty %2$s information to avoid personal information leakage.
Note: This may affect the use of some app features.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_all_open_context
items.zh:
开启后，系统将提供虚拟%1$s代替真实%2$s，避免个人信息泄露。
注意：部分应用可能无法正常使用。
items.en:
When turned on, the system will provide virtual %1$s instead of real %2$s to avoid the leakage of personal information.
Note: Some apps may not work properly.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_auto_config_switch_dialog
items.zh:
开启后，系统将为您自动判断是否要对应用开启保护，被保护项将以空信息代替真实信息。
注意：部分应用可能无法正常使用。
items.en:
Smart Protection will automatically determine whether or not to turn on protection for an app. Items that are protected will have real information replaced by empty information.
Note: This may affect the use of some app features.

items.name: name:settings_dc_backlight_mode_tip
items.zh: 开启后，在屏幕低亮度下，可降低屏幕闪烁产生的视觉疲劳感，但屏幕会增加少量噪点。
items.en: Reduce the visual fatigue caused by screen flicker at a low screen brightness level. This will slightly increase image noise.

items.name: name:settings_dc_backlight_mode_tip_new
items.zh: 开启后，在屏幕低亮度下，可降低屏幕闪烁产生的视觉疲劳感。
items.en: When turned on, it can reduce the visual fatigue caused by screen flickering at a low screen brightness level.

items.name: name:description_ocr_for_bigtouch
items.zh: 开启后，在未获取到文字时将通过图像识别方式提取内容
items.en: When this is on, contents will be extracted through image recognition when no text is obtained

items.name: name:dialog_msg_close_ocr_for_find_text
items.zh: 开启后，在系统未直接获取文字时将通过图像识别方式提取内容。
items.en: When this is on, contents will be extracted through image recognition when no text is directly obtained by the system.

items.name: name:resizeable_screen_summary
items.zh: 开启后，在支持分屏的应用下，长按多任务键可进入分屏
items.en: When turned on, hold down the Multitask Button to enter split-screen mode in apps that support this function

items.name: name:resizeable_screen_summary
items.zh: 开启后，在支持分屏的应用下，长按多任务键可进入分屏。
items.en: When turned on, touch and hold the Recent button to enter the Split Screen mode in apps that support this function.

items.name: name:turn_on_hint
items.zh: 开启后，智能调整应用页面为暗色效果。若应用自身已有暗色模式，建议关闭以减少冲突。
items.en: Turn on the switch to set an app to Dark Mode. If an app has its own dark mode, you can turn its switch off.

items.name: name:dual_clock_desktop_world_tips
items.zh: 开启后，桌面将显示所有已添加的世界时钟。
items.en: Display any world clocks you add on the Home screen.

items.name: name:mark_pref_summery_allow_background_run
items.zh: 开启后会导致功耗增加
items.en: More power is consumed when this is on.

items.name: name:summary_create_shortcut
items.zh: 开启后可从桌面快捷进入，若不再需要快捷方式可以从桌面长按删除。
items.en: When turned on, quick access is available on homescreen. If quick access is no longer required, simply touch and hold to delete it.

items.name: name:sla_effect_prompt_enabled
items.zh: 开启后可显著提升网速
items.en: Network Speed Can Be Significantly Increased When It Is Turned On

items.name: name:wakeup_by_speech_introduce
items.zh: 开启后可以使用以下唤醒词唤醒语音助手:
items.en: When this function is on, you can use the following wakeup words to wake up Voice Assistant.

items.name: name:super_power_save_content_fla
items.zh: 开启后可在右上角菜单中退出
items.en: To turn this mode off, tap the button in the upper right corner.

items.name: name:use_technical_standard_icons_summary
items.zh: 开启后列表图标将使用简化技术标准样式
items.en: Turn on to use a simplified version of the Wi-Fi Alliance icon.

items.name: name:settings_notification_guide_msg
items.zh: 开启后你可以通过手表接收手机的推送通知
items.en: Receive notifications directly on your watch.

items.name: name:high_performance_message
items.zh: 开启后手机将始终保持高性能运作，会额外增加功耗，可能出现发热。
items.en: When turned on, more power will be consumed and your phone may overheat.

items.name: name:high_performance_message_ch
items.zh: 开启后手机将始终保持高性能运作，会额外增加耗电，可能出现发热。
items.en: When turned on, more power will be consumed and your device may overheat.

items.name: name:broadcast_introduce
items.zh: 开启后语音助手将使用声音回复你。
items.en: Voice Assistant will respond to you verbally.

items.name: name:nfc_switch_summary
items.zh: 开启后允许手机在触碰其他设备时交换数据
items.en: Turn on to allow for exchanging data between devices in close proximity.

items.name: name:nfc_android_beam_closed_summary_new
items.zh: 开启后允许通过 NFC 连接传输数据
items.en: When turned on, connection for data transfer via NFC is allowed

items.name: name:auto_notification_des
items.zh: 开启后执行指令时将收到通知
items.en: Receive a notification when an action is executed.

items.name: name:protect_eye_mode_introducation
items.zh: 开启护眼模式可降低屏幕蓝光辐射，预防用眼疲劳。
items.en: Eye Care reduces blue light from the screen and prevents eye strain.

items.name: name:pref_key_information_receiving_range_summary
items.zh: 开启即接收非通讯录联系人的网络信息
items.en: Receive network messages from people not in your contacts.

items.name: name:notification_content_guide
items.zh: 开启密码本，可保存和自动填充应用的帐号和密码
items.en: Turn on Passwords to automatically store your account passwords for autofill.

items.name: name:please_close_wifi
items.zh: 开启免费专属流量，需关闭当前 WLAN 网络，是否开启？
items.en: Current Wi-Fi Network Will Need to Be Turned Off in Order to Turn On Free Exclusive Data. Turn It On?

items.name: name:player_screen_On_tip
items.en: Screen rotation and buttons are enabled

items.name: name:permission_manager_content
items.zh: 开启权限监控，可以保护手机的隐私和数据，建议开启
items.en: Turn on permission monitoring for privacy and data protection.

items.name: name:oppo_oppen_block_settings_tips
items.zh: 开启骚扰拦截设置，拦截骚扰来电
items.en: Turn on Block & Filter to block unwanted calls.

items.name: name:oppo_screen_pinning_disable_for_gesture
items.zh: 开启上滑手势导航后，屏幕固定显示功能将无法使用
items.en: When Swipe-up Gestures is on, Screen Pinning will be unavailable.

items.name: name:oppo_screen_pinning_disable_for_gesture
items.zh: 开启上滑手势导航后，屏幕固定显示功能将无法使用。
items.en: When Swipe-up Gesture Navigation is on, the Screen Pinning function will not be available.

items.name: name:power_saving_mode_warning_summary_no_item
items.zh: 开启省电模式，对耗电项目进行优化。
items.en: Turn on Power saving mode for the following optimizations:

items.name: name:power_saving_mode_warning_summary_new
items.zh: 开启省电模式时，将进行以下耗电项目的优化。
items.en: Turn on Power saving mode for the following optimizations:

items.name: name:power_saving_mode_warnning_summary
items.zh:
开启省电模式时：
1.将关闭后台应用，暂停后台自动同步功能；
2.将降低屏幕亮度；
3.关闭触摸振动。
items.en:
When Power Saving Mode is turned on, the system will:
1. Quit background apps and pause background auto sync. 
2. Lower screen brightness. 
3. Turn off Vibrate on Touch.

items.name: name:power_saving_mode_warnning_summary
items.zh:
开启省电模式时：
1.将暂停后台自动同步功能；
2.将降低屏幕亮度；
3.关闭触摸振动。
items.en:
Power Saving Mode conserves battery power by:
1. Pausing background auto sync. 
2. Reducing screen brightness. 
3. Turning off Vibrate on Touch.

items.name: name:power_saving_mode_warning_summary_5g
items.zh:
开启省电模式时：
1.将暂停后台自动同步功能；
2.将降低屏幕亮度；
3.关闭触摸振动；
4.智能切换5G网络。
items.en:
Power Saving Mode conserves battery power by:
1. Pausing background auto sync. 
2. Reducing screen brightness. 
3. Turning off Vibrate on Touch. 
4. Automatically switching between 4G and 5G.

items.name: name:glove_mode_summary
items.zh: 开启手套模式后，即使带着手套，您依然可以操作屏幕 （充电或者连接USB时，手套模式失效）
items.en: When 'Gloves mode' is enabled, you can operate the touch screen with gloves on (Gloves mode will not be effective during charging or when the phone is connected with USB)

items.name: name:add_fence_reminder
items.zh: 开启守护范围后对方手机将持续开启GPS定位，耗电量有所增加。
items.en: After the scope of guard is turned on, GPS positioning will be constantly enabled on the other party's phone, which will increase power consumption.

items.name: name:online_guide_info_enable
items.zh: 开启锁屏杂志，海量图片即刻在眼前
items.en: Abundant images are available with lockscreen magazine enabled

items.name: name:sim_call_forwarding_open_tip
items.zh: 开启无人接听时转接，当手机主卡号码无人接听时，该电话会转接到你输入的手表号码
items.en: When a call to the primary mobile phone number is not answered, the call will be forwarded to the watch number you set.

items.name: name:pilot_title
items.en: Turn On Purchase Without Network Service

items.name: name:accessibility_color_mode_desc
items.zh: 开启无障碍颜色模式后，部分系统主题色改变为白色背景下对比度更高的颜色，以提高其可阅读性。
items.en: Once turned on, some theme colors have a higher contrast against the white background, making texts easier to read.

items.name: name:privacy_update_service_title
items.zh: 开启系统安全更新服务

items.name: name:protect_eye_mode_introducation
items.zh: 开启夜间护眼可降低屏幕蓝光辐射，预防用眼疲劳。
items.en: Turn on Night Shield to reduce blue light from the screen, thus preventing eye strain.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_tip_info
items.zh: 开启隐私保护后，系统将提供虚拟%1$s代替真实%2$s，避免个人信息泄露。
items.en: When Privacy Protection is turned on, the system will provide virtual %1$s instead of real %2$s to avoid the leakage of personal information.

items.name: name:settings_open_background_permission
items.zh: 开启应用后台运行权限，避免设备断开连接，通知推送和数据同步不及时。
items.en: Turn on background activity permissions to prevent device disconnection and ensure that notifications and data sync are not delayed.

items.name: name:wakeup_open_tip
items.zh: 开启语音唤醒会减少手表续航，建议在不使用时关闭该功能。
items.en: Turning on Voice wakeup will reduce the battery life of your watch. We recommend turning this feature off when you are not using it.

items.name: name:open_cloud_switch_to_store_contacts
items.zh: 开启云服务，将联系人保存到云端
items.en: Turn on cloud service to save your contacts to the cloud.

items.name: name:open_heytap_cloud_to_store_contacts

items.name: name:instruction_about_mic
items.zh: 录屏功能的麦克风默认处于关闭状态。除非您主动打开麦克风，否则不会录制录屏过程中的语音；如您选择主动打开麦克风，意味着您知悉且理解您所在地区关于个人数据与隐私保护等相关法律法规的规定，并独立承担由所收录的声音（和视频）信息可能引起的法律责任；
items.en: The microphone is turned off by default for the screen recording function. No voice will be recorded during screen recording unless you choose to turn on the microphone. If you choose to turn on the microphone, it shall be deemed that you know and understand the local laws and regulations of the area you are in regarding data and privacy protection, and that you are solely responsible for any liabilities arising from your recording of audios (and videos);

items.name: name:statement_page_about_mic
items.zh: 录屏功能的麦克风默认处于关闭状态。除非您主动打开麦克风，否则录屏功能不会录制麦克风声音；如您选择主动打开麦克风，意味着您知悉且理解您所在地区关于私人通信自由与通信秘密保护、个人数据与隐私保护等相关法律法规的规定，并独立承担由所收录的声音（和视频）信息可能引起的法律责任；
items.en: By default, the microphone is turned off in the Screen Recording function. Unless you turn on the microphone yourself, the Screen Recording feature will not record microphone sounds. If you choose to turn on the microphone, you are deemed to have understood and acknowledged the provisions of your location's relevant laws and regulations for the protection of freedom of private communication & privacy of correspondence, and protection of personal data & privacy, you are also solely responsible for all legal liabilities arising from your audio (and video) recordings.

items.name: name:instruction_about_sys_audio
items.zh: 录屏功能的系统音录制默认处于关闭状态。除非您主动打开系统音录制开关，否则不会录制录屏过程中的系统声音；如您选择主动打开系统音录制，意味着您知悉且理解您所在地区关于个人数据与隐私保护等相关法律法规的规定，并独立承担由所收录的系统音（和视频）信息可能引起的法律责任；
items.en: Recording of system sound is turned off by default for the screen recording function. No system sound will be recorded during screen recording unless you choose to turn on system sound recording. If you choose to turn on system sound recording, it shall be deemed that you know and understand the local laws and regulations of the area you are in regarding data and privacy protection, and that you are solely responsible for any liabilities arising from your recording of the system sound (and videos);

items.name: name:statement_page_about_sys_audio
items.zh: 录屏功能的系统音录制默认处于关闭状态。除非您主动打开系统音录制开关，否则录屏功能不会录制系统声音；如您选择主动打开系统音录制，意味着您知悉且理解您所在地区关于私人通信自由与通信秘密保护、个人数据与隐私保护等相关法律法规的规定，并独立承担由所收录的声音（和视频）信息可能引起的法律责任；
items.en: Recording of system sound is turned off by default for the screen recording function. You cannot use the screen recording function to record any system sound unless you choose to actively turn on the switch of recording of system sound, if you choose to actively turn on the switch of recording of system sound, it means that you acknowledge and understand the provisions of the relevant laws and regulations in your area relating to the protection of freedom of private communication & privacy of correspondence, and protection of personal data & privacy, and that you are solely responsible for any liabilities arising from your recording audios (and videos),

items.name: name:statement_page_head
items.zh: 录屏功能可以让您轻松收录屏幕显示的内容以及您的操作过程，以形成自己录制的屏幕视频。在您主动开启麦克风的情况下，录屏功能还可以收录您在录屏过程中的语音讲解及系统音。
items.en: The Screen Recording function lets you easily record content displayed on your screen as well as your operations, creating your own videos of the screen. If you turn on the microphone, Screen Recording can also record your speech and system sounds during the recording.

items.name: name:statement_head
items.zh: 录屏功能可以让您轻松收录屏幕显示的内容以及您的操作过程，以形成自己录制的屏幕视频。在您主动开启麦克风的情况下，录屏功能还可以收录您在录屏过程中的语音讲解及系统音。
items.en: Screen recording lets you easily record what is displayed on the screen and your operations to create your own screen videos. If you have the microphone turned on, screen recording can also record the system sound and what you say during the screen recording process into the video.

items.name: name:instruction_introduction_sys_audio
items.zh: 录屏功能可以让您轻松收录智能手机屏幕显示的内容以及您的屏幕操作过程。在您主动开启麦克风和系统音录制开关的情况下，还可以收录在录屏过程中的语音及系统音。
items.en: Screen Recording enables you to easily record contents displayed on the screen of your phone and screen operations you performed. If you have turned on Record Microphone Sound and Record System Sound, your voice and the system sound will also be recorded during screen recording.

items.name: name:instruction_introduction
items.zh: 录屏功能可以让您轻松收录智能手机屏幕显示的内容以及您的屏幕操作过程。在您主动开启麦克风录制开关的情况下，还可以收录在录屏过程中的语音。
items.en: Screen Recording enables you to easily record the content displayed on the screen of your phone and the screen operations you performed. If you have turned on Record Microphone Sound, your voice will also be recorded during screen recording.

items.name: name:default_print_service_description

items.name: name:str_ipmsg_spam_empty
items.zh:
您当前黑名单聊天列表没有内容。 
这里显示所有被标记为“黑名单”的聊天会话。被标记为黑名单的会话聊天的消息提示默认会被关掉，它能阻止一些不必要的骚扰 。 

您可以长按一个聊天会话，并通过点击黑名单菜单标记它为黑名单。 当一个聊天会话被标记为黑名单时，聊天会话上会显示一个无信息提示图标，该聊天会话同时会被放到当前黑名单列表。
items.en:
You don't have any spam conversation. 
SPAM collects all conversations that are marked as spam. Notification will be turned off by default. This avoid you from unnecessary disturbance. 

You can mark a sender as spam by holding a conversation and selecting Mark as Spam icon. When a conversation is marked as spam, a notification-off icon will be shown automatically and the conversation will be placed here.

items.name: name:no_arrive_content
items.zh: 您当前可能尚未到达目的地，继续开启可能失败，如成功则开始计时。确定要启用吗？
items.en: You probably have not yet arrived at your destination, so this function may fail to turn on, otherwise, time will start counting. Are you sure to enable?

items.name: name:str_ipmsg_groupchat_empty
items.zh:
您当前群组聊天列表没有内容。
这里显示所有的您所创建或参与的群组聊天会话。在这里您可以很容易找到并管理您的群组聊天。

点击屏幕下方的“创建群组”按钮，您可以创建一个群组，并邀请您的好友加入群组。
items.en:
You don't have any group chat message. 
GROUP CHATS collects all group chat messages that are created or joined by you. This allows you find and manage your group chats easily. 

To create a group chat, you can tap on Create a group chat button at the bottom of this screen and invite your friends to join the group.

items.name: name:qrcode_setting_private_message

items.en: Your Personal Profile Is Not Set Currently. Set Up Now?

items.name: name:str_ipmsg_important_empty
items.zh:
您当前重要聊天列表没有内容。
这里显示所有您标记为“重要”的信息所在的聊天会话，在这里您可以很容易的看到被标记为“重要”的信息。

您可以长按一条信息，在菜单中选择“标为重要”，把这条信息标记为“重要”。当这条信息被标记为重要，在这条信息的下方，您会看到一个小红旗。
items.en:
You don't have any important message. 
IMPORTANT collects all the messages that are flagged as important. This allows you find important messages easily. 

You can flag a message as important by holding a message and selecting Flag as important from Option menu. When a message is flagged as important, you will see a red flag icon as below.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_2
items.zh: 您可以通过多种不同的方式使用我们的服务，例如使用ColorOS产品、服务等。如果您与我们分享信息，我们就能为您提供更好的服务，如显示相关程度更高的产品更新和广告、帮助您与他人联系或者更轻松快捷地与他人分享内容等。基于此目的，我们将向您解释我们对信息的收集和使用方式，以及您可采用什么方式来保护自己的隐私权。
items.en: You can enjoy our services in a variety of different ways. For example, you might log into the OPPO website to buy and use OPPO products and services. Any information you share with us (e.g., in the process of creating an OPPO ID) will help us to improve our services to you. Using this information, we are able to share product updates and serve you advertisements according to your interests, as well as help you contact and share content more easily with people in your network. Read the following to understand how we collect and use the information you choose to share with us, and find out how you can protect your privacy.

items.name: name:instruction_storage

Without your prior consent, OPPO will not upload any of your screen recording data to the servers of OPPO, eliminating the possibility of disclosing such data to any other third party or using it for any other purpose.

Without your prior and explicit consent, OPPO will not upload any of your screen videos to the company servers, this eliminates the possibility of these information being revealed to any third-party or used for any other purposes.

items.name: name:health_light_sleep_desc
items.zh: 浅睡过程中，脑电波、呼吸频率和心率会略有减慢。在此睡眠阶段，⼈容易被唤醒，并且浅睡对缓解人疲劳的作用甚微。睡眠过程中，浅睡时长的占比不宜超过55%。
items.en: Light sleep is a sleep stage in which your brain waves, breathing, and heartbeat slow down only slightly. You can be easily awoken during this stage and it is not as refreshing as deep sleep. Light sleep should take up no more than 55% of one's sleep cycle.

items.name: name:change_partiton_warning_1
items.zh: 切换分区功能是为了解决安装较多程序后出现的存储空间不足的问题。首次成功切换分区后，您的手机存储将从出厂默认的分区模式，切换到统一分区模式。在统一分区模式下，应用程序的安装空间将不再受到默认分区下的限制，从而使您可以安装更多的应用；再次点击切换分区可以将分区恢复为出厂默认的分区模式。
items.en: Switching partitions can solve the problem of insufficient storage space caused by the installation of too many apps. When you switch the partitions successfully for the first time, your storage mode will changed from the default factory mode to the integrated mode. In this mode, installation space for apps will not be limited by the default partitions, therefore you can install more apps. Tap switch partitions again to restore partitions to the default factory mode.

items.name: name:network_message_about_info
items.zh:
"什么是“网络信息”？
“网络信息”是信息接收与发送的增强功能，用户可以通过数据或 WLAN 网络发送文字、图片、语音与视频等消息，同时支持品牌服务号通过信息发送和接收，向用户提供便捷服务。

“网络信息”的优势？
使用“网络信息”功能，
 1. 用户可以通过数据或 WLAN 免费给同样开启并使用手机号码激活网络信息的 OPPO 用户发送文字、图片、语音和视频；向不支持网络信息或未激活的用户发送信息，运营商将收取费用。
 2. 用户可以免费通过网络信息与品牌服务号互动，获取服务号提供的线上咨询、信息和便捷服务等。
 * OPPO 用户使用网络信息的发送功能，需要开启网络信息功能并使用手机号码激活网络信息，如未使用手机号激活网络信息，则只能接收品牌服务号向自己发送的信息。

如何开启、关闭和切换手机卡使用“网络信息”功能？

items.name:
开启条件：1. 打开“网络信息”功能，并选择手机卡使用手机号码进行激活注册；2. 手机号码激活成功后，即可完整使用网络信息的接收和发送服务。
开启与关闭：通过设置“网络信息”开关状态，开启和关闭功能。
切换手机卡使用“网络信息”功能：可在“设置-信息-网络信息-接收与发送”中，重新选择手机卡进行功能激活后，即可使用该手机号码发送“网络信息”。"
items.application:
What is the Network Messaging Service?
The network messaging service allows users to send and receive text messages, images, audios, or videos via Wi-Fi or the mobile network. This feature also allows service providers to send and receive messages to provide a range of services to users.

What are the Advantages of the Network Messaging Service?
With this feature:
1. Users will be able to use Wi-Fi or the mobile network to send text messages, images, audios, and videos free of charge to other OPPO users who have also used their mobile numbers to activate network messaging. (Carrier charges may apply if you send messages to users who are not using the network messaging service.)
2. Users will be able to interact with service providers via official service accounts to enjoy a range of services.
* In order to send messages to service accounts, you have to enable the network messaging service and activate the service with your mobile number. If you haven't activated this feature with your mobile number, you will only be able to receive messages from service accounts.

How to Enable and Disable the Network Messaging Service or Use this Service with a Different Phone Number
Enable this service: 1. Turn on the network messaging service and activate it with your mobile number; 2.You will be able to send and receive network messages after activation.
Disable this service:
Turn off the Network Messaging Service switch.
Use this service with a different number: Go to "Settings - Messages - Network Messaging Service - Send & Receive", and activate the network messaging service with a different number.

items.en: Information to the habit of use and the discovery of problems - When you join the ColorOS "User Experience Improvement Program", statistics of your use of the functions of the products are gathered anonymously on an as-needed basis, through which user habit related information are obtained covering the use of the ColorOS official website, products and services. When an abnormal exit or a crash occurs in the system, we will collect information on the current condition of the mobile phone to facilitate diagnosis of the issue.

数据服务平台是通过感知-认知-决策链条，为用户提供基于情境的个性化服务，包括通勤提醒、电影取票提醒、电影静音提醒、行程提醒、关闭设备提醒、到家提醒、离家提醒、淘宝跳转等功能的软件。为了实现前述目的，我们在向您提供服务时，可能需要收集或从独立的应用程序或功能中同步您提供的或您设备的相关信息（包括但不限于个人信息），例如：
1、为了识别当前所使用该功能的设备及进行设备安全控制，我们需要获得您的设备信息（如：IMEI）；
2、为了向您提供个性化的智能信息服务，您需要注册或登录 HeyTap 帐号，HeyTap 帐号可能会要求您提供个人信息,如手机号码、电子邮箱、帐号名称及密码等，您在注册 HeyTap 帐号时，需要另行同意《HeyTap 帐号隐私声明》。同时，我们需要获取您的 HeyTap 帐号、昵称及头像，以便在数据服务平台中显示；
3、为了向您提供“上下班通勤建议”的功能，我们需要获得您的位置信息；
4、为了向您提供“会议静音建议”的功能 ，我们需要分析您的日程信息，通过语义识别相关的第三方服务提供方，识别出会议类型的日程，以便在相应的时间提醒您将手机静音。
5、为了向您提供飞机、火车、电影、酒店、快递等服务，我们需要在您的设备本地分析您的短信信息，但我们仅将分析结果上传至服务器，以便更新最新的服务信息，及时向您呈现。如，我们会获得您的航班信息，并向您提供行程展示及查询服务；
6、为了优化产品功能，个性化您的用户体验，我们会根据大部分用户的使用习惯数据，优化我们的界面布局逻辑，使得软件界面布局更合理，我们需要获取您的操作行为数据，如产品功能使用统计数据。
我们将严格遵守前述载明的目的来使用您的个人信息，您的个人信息将仅用于收集时即已确定并且经过您同意的目的，如有除此之外的任何其他用途，我们都会提前征得您的同意。同时，我们将采取一切合理可行的有针对性的组织和技术措施，以保护您的个人信息，防止其遭到未经授权的访问、公开披露、使用、修改、损坏或丢失。例如，我们会使用加密技术确保数据传输、存储的安全性。
%1$s如将您的位置信息分享给地图服务提供商，以便为您提供通勤服务。将您的航班信息分享给航班信息服务提供商，以便您查看您的航班状态。除本说明载明的情况外，未经您的同意，我们将不会向第三方披露您的个人信息，用于其各自的独立市场营销或商业用途。
如果您需要使用第三方服务提供商提供的服务，第三方可能会收集您的信息。我们无法控制第三方的隐私和数据保护政策，此类第三方不受到本协议的约束。您在向第三方提交个人数据之前，请阅读这些第三方的隐私保护政策。
在您停止使用数据服务平台的某些功能后，数据服务平台将停止收集或同步您与这些功能有关的个人信息。
如果您不同意我们采集上述信息，您可以点击“不同意”关闭数据服务平台，但这将导致本软件无法正常运行，我们将无法为您提供服务。在您启用数据服务平台后，您可以通过访问“设置-应用管理-数据服务平台-清除数据”来终止数据服务平台继续处理您的数据。
若您点击“同意”以启用数据服务平台功能，意味着您充分明确地了解上述的信息收集和使用行为（包括但不限于其范围、方式、目的与期限等）以及您所拥有的权利等事宜，并同意我们收集和使用您提供的和您的设备的相关信息。
针对数据服务平台功能所涉及的个人信息，本说明未列明的具体隐私政策事宜（包括但不限于“第三方信息”、“我们如何保护您的个人信息”、“您的权利”、“我们如何处理儿童的个人信息”、“您的个人信息如何在全球范围转移”等），请参照并以我们的隐私政策为准。%2$s
items.en:
Thanks to its perception-cognition-decision chain, the Data Services Platform can provide users with scenario-based, personalized services, including reminders to commute, collect movie tickets, silent your phone for movies, itinerary, turn off your device, and when you arrive or leave the home or to go to Taobao or other apps. To this end, when we provide services to you, we may need to collect or synchronize from separate applications or functions information that you provide or information related to your device (including but not limited to personal information), such as:
1. To identify the device that is currently using this function and to monitor device security, we need to get your device information (such as the IMEI);
2. For us to provide you with smart personalized messaging services, you need to register or sign in with a HeyTap Account. This may require you to provide personal information, such as a mobile number, e-mail, account name and password. When you register a HeyTap Account, you are required to separately agree to the HeyTap Account Privacy Statement. At the same time, we need to get your HeyTap Account, display name, and profile photo to display in Data Services Platform;
3. We need to get your location information to provide you with commuting suggestions;
4. In order to provide you with the "Silent During Meeting Reminder" function, we need to analyze your schedule information, identify relevant third-party service providers through semantics, and identify the schedule for the meeting type, so as to remind you to set your phone to silent at the corresponding time.
5. To provide you with services such as flights, trains, movies, hotels and express deliveries, we need to analyze your SMS messages locally on your device, but we will only upload the analysis results to the server to update the latest service information and present it to you in time. For example, we will get your flight information to display your itinerary and offer you query services;
6. To optimize the product function and personalize your user experience, we will optimize the layout logic of our interface based on the usage habit data of most users to make the layout of our software interface more reasonable. To do this, we need to get data about your operational behavior, such as product function usage statistics
We will strictly abide by the purpose stated in the aforementioned when your personal information is used. Your personal information will only be used for the purposes that have been established at the time of collection with your consent. In the event that such information may be used for any other purposes, we will seek your prior consent before we proceed. Meanwhile, we will take all reasonable, feasible and pertinent organizational and technical measures to protect your personal information to prevent unauthorized access, public disclosure, use, modification, damage or loss. For example, we will use encryption technology to ensure security of data transmission and storage.
%1$sFor example, we may share your location information with mapping service providers in order to provide you with commuting services. We may share your flight information with the flight information service provider so that you can check your flight status. Unless otherwise stated in this statement, we will not disclose your personal information to third parties without your prior consent for their respective independent marketing or commercial use.
If you need to use services provided by third-party service providers, the third parties may collect your information. We have no control over third-party privacy and data protection policies as such third parties are not bound by this Agreement. Before you submit personal data to third parties, please read their privacy protection policies.
Once you have stopped using certain functions of Data Services Platform, the platform will stop collecting or syncing your personal information related to these functions
If you do not agree to us collecting the above information, you can tap "No" to close Data Services Platform, however this will cause the app to run improperly, and we will be unable to provide you with the services. After you have turned on the Data Services Platform, you can stop the platform from processing your data by accessing Settings - App Management - Data Services Platform - Clear Data.
If you tap "Agree" to enable the Data Services Platform functions, it means that you fully understand the above-mentioned on information collection and use (including but not limited to its scope, method, purpose and timeline), and on matters such as your rights, and you agree that we can collect and use the information that you have provided and information related to your device.
In view of the personal information involved in the Data Services Platform functions, for any specific privacy policy matter that has not been explicitly mentioned in this statement (including but not limited to "third-party information", "how we protect your personal information", "your rights", "how we handle personal information of minors", "how your personal information is transmitted globally"), please refer to our privacy policy. %2$s

针对数据服务平台功能所涉及的个人信息，本说明未列明的具体隐私政策事宜（包括但不限于“第三方信息”、“我们如何保护您的个人信息”、“您的权利”、“我们如何处理儿童的个人信息”、“您的个人信息如何在全球范围转移”等），请参照并以我们的隐私政策为准。%2$s

items.name: name:statement_content_oppo_v2
items.zh:
数据服务平台是通过感知-认知-决策链条，为用户提供基于情境的个性化服务的软件，支持的模块包括“Breeno 建议”（如通勤提醒、电影取票提醒、电影静音提醒、行程提醒、关闭设备提醒、到家提醒、离家提醒）、“Breeno 语音”、“Breeno 速览”“Breeno 指令”、“日历”。为了实现前述目的，我们在向您提供服务时，可能需要收集或从独立的应用程序或功能中同步您提供的或您设备的相关信息（包括但不限于个人信息），例如：
1、为了识别当前所使用该功能的设备及进行设备安全控制，我们需要获得您的设备信息（如：IMEI）；
2、为了向您提供个性化的智能信息服务，您需要注册或登录 OPPO 帐号，OPPO 帐号可能会要求您提供个人信息,如手机号码、电子邮箱、帐号名称及密码等，您在注册 OPPO 帐号时，需要另行同意《OPPO 帐号隐私声明》。同时，我们需要获取您的 OPPO 帐号、昵称及头像，以便在数据服务平台中显示；
3、为了向您提供“上下班通勤建议”的功能，我们需要获得您的位置信息；
4、为了向您提供“会议静音建议”的功能 ，我们需要分析您的日程信息，通过语义识别相关的第三方服务提供方，识别出会议类型的日程，以便在相应的时间提醒您将手机静音。
5、为了向您提供飞机、火车、电影、酒店、快递等服务，我们需要在您的设备本地分析您的短信信息，但我们仅将分析结果上传至服务器，以便更新最新的服务信息，及时向您呈现。如，我们会获得您的航班信息，并向您提供行程展示及查询服务；
6、为了优化产品功能，个性化您的用户体验，我们会根据大部分用户的使用习惯数据，优化我们的界面布局逻辑，使得软件界面布局更合理，我们需要获取您的操作行为数据，如产品功能使用统计数据。
我们将严格遵守前述载明的目的来使用您的个人信息，您的个人信息将仅用于收集时即已确定并且经过您同意的目的，如有除此之外的任何其他用途，我们都会提前征得您的同意。同时，我们将采取一切合理可行的有针对性的组织和技术措施，以保护您的个人信息，防止其遭到未经授权的访问、公开披露、使用、修改、损坏或丢失。例如，我们会使用加密技术确保数据传输、存储的安全性。
%1$s如将您的位置信息分享给地图服务提供商，以便为您提供通勤服务。将您的航班信息分享给航班信息服务提供商，以便您查看您的航班状态。除本说明载明的情况外，未经您的同意，我们将不会向第三方披露您的个人信息，用于其各自的独立市场营销或商业用途。
如果您需要使用第三方服务提供商提供的服务，第三方可能会收集您的信息。我们无法控制第三方的隐私和数据保护政策，此类第三方不受到本协议的约束。您在向第三方提交个人数据之前，请阅读这些第三方的隐私保护政策。
在您停止使用数据服务平台的某些功能后，数据服务平台将停止收集或同步您与这些功能有关的个人信息。
如果您不同意我们采集上述信息，您可以点击“不同意”关闭数据服务平台，但这将导致本软件无法正常运行，我们将无法为您提供服务。在您启用数据服务平台后，您可以通过访问“设置-应用管理-数据服务平台-清除数据”来终止数据服务平台继续处理您的数据。
若您点击“同意”以启用数据服务平台功能，意味着您充分明确地了解上述的信息收集和使用行为（包括但不限于其范围、方式、目的与期限等）以及您所拥有的权利等事宜，并同意我们收集和使用您提供的和您的设备的相关信息。
针对数据服务平台功能所涉及的个人信息，本说明未列明的具体隐私政策事宜（包括但不限于“第三方信息”、“我们如何保护您的个人信息”、“您的权利”、“我们如何处理儿童的个人信息”、“您的个人信息如何在全球范围转移”等），请参照并以我们的隐私政策为准。%2$s

items.name: name:South_Pole_Detail
items.zh: "它被人们称为第七大陆，是地球上最后一个被发现，唯一没有人员定居的大陆。它的总面积为1390

items.name: 万平方千米，相当于中国和印巴次大陆面积的总和，居世界各洲第五位。整个南极大陆被一个巨大的冰盖所覆盖，平均海拔为2350米，是世界上最高的大陆。南极洲蕴藏的矿物有220余种。"
items.application: Called the 7th continent, it was the last continent to be discovered and the only one without a permanent human settlement. It spans approximately 13.9 million km2, equal to the combined areas of China, India, and Pakistan, making it the fifth largest continent in the world. The landmass is completely covered by ice sheets. It is also the world's highest continent, with an average elevation of 2.35 km. Antarctica also contains deposits of 220 kinds of minerals.

items.name: name:Mount_Everest_Detail
items.zh: "它是地球第一高峰，属于喜马拉雅山脉，位于中国西藏自治区与尼泊尔萨加玛塔专区边界上。2005年中国国家测绘局测量的岩面高为8,844.43米，尼泊尔则使用传统的雪盖高8,

items.name: 848米。它除了是海拔最高的山峰之外，也是距离地心第五远的高峰。"
items.application: The highest mountain on Earth, located in the Himalayas on the border between Tibet Autonomous Region in China and the Sagarmatha Zone in Nepal. In 2005, China's State Bureau of Surveying and Mapping measured its rock height to be 8,844.43 m, whereas Nepal uses the traditional snow height of 8,848 m. In addition to being the highest mountain above sea level, its summit is the fifth farthest from Earth's center.

items.name: name:Olympia_Undae_Detail
items.zh: "它是火星北极区的一个广大的沙丘地，是火星表面最广大的连续沙丘地，其面积与阿拉伯半岛上的鲁卜哈利沙漠相当。它位于火星北极高原外围，范围包括东经120°到240°，北纬78°到83

items.name: °的广大沙漠，延伸约1100公里，面积47万平方公里。"
items.application: A vast dune field in the north polar region of the planet Mars. The largest continuous dune field on Mars, it is similar in size to the Rub' Al Khali in the Arabian Peninsula. It partly rings the north polar plateau from about 120° to 240°E longitude and 78° to 83°N latitude. Stretching about 1,100 km across and covering an area of 470,000 km2.

items.name: name:Olympus_Mon_Detail
items.zh: 它是火星上的盾状火山，亦为太阳系中已知最高的山，高于基准面21,229米，将近地球冒纳罗亚火山从海底算起高度（9公里多）的两倍多，且两者同样都是盾状火山，山顶也都有破火山口。
items.en: A very large shield volcano on the planet Mars and the tallest planetary mountain in the Solar System. It has a height of nearly 22 km, more than twice as tall as Mauna Loa as measured from the sea floor. This comparison is apt, as both are shield volcanoes with calderas at their peaks.

items.name: name:American_Cordillera_Detail
items.zh: 它是世界上最长的山系，其山脉位于南北美洲大陆西部，北起阿拉斯加，南到火地岛，绵延约1.5万公里。其构造极为复杂，由一系列褶皱断层组成，地壳活动至今仍在继续，多火山、地震，是环太平洋火山地震带重要组成部分。它拥有多种矿产资源，堪称“矿产宝库”。
items.en: The longest sequence of mountain ranges in the world, located along the west side of North and South America. It stretches about 15,000 km, from as far north as Alaska to as far south as Tierra del Fuego. Its structure is complex, being composed of a series of folds and faults, with tectonic activity still occurring to this day. With its many volcanoes and earthquakes, it makes up a core component of the Pacific Ring of Fire. As it also houses many different kinds of mineral deposits, it is known as a "treasure trove" of minerals.

items.name: name:Sahara_Desert_Detail
items.zh: 它是世界最热的荒漠，亦是世界第三大荒漠，仅次于南极和北极，同时也是世界上最大的沙漠，其总面积超过9,400,000平方千米，与美国国土面积相当。
items.en: The largest hot desert in the world, and the third largest desert overall after Antarctica and the Arctic. Its area of 9,400,000 square kilometers is comparable to the area of the United States.

items.name: name:Mare_Crisium_Detail
items.zh: "它是位于月球正面东部危海盆地中的一座月海，面积近17

items.name: .6万平方公里，表面极为平坦。它是月球正面最孤独的月海：四周环被辽阔的高地环抱，仅间杂着一些零碎的小月海区。该月海中分布有质量瘤、皱岭和撞击坑等特征，但没有类似月溪的地堑。"
items.application: Located in the Crisium basin in the eastern portion of the near side of the Moon, it is 176,000 km2 in area and has a very flat floor. The most isolated mare on the near side of the Moon, it is surrounded by vast uplands on all sides interspersed with smaller, scattered mares. A mass concentration (mascon), impact crater, and wrinkle ridges were identified in the center of Mare Crisium, but no rilles or other channels were found.

items.name: name:Great_Red_Spot_Detail
items.zh: 它是一个已在木星赤道以南22°存在了很久的巨大反气旋风暴。它呈现红色的原因尚不是很清楚，当前实验室的实验支持的理论为：红色是由复杂的有机分子，像是红磷或其它的硫化物所造成。
items.en: A persistent high-pressure region in the atmosphere of Jupiter, producing an anticyclonic storm, the largest in the Solar System, 22 degrees south of Jupiter's equator. It is not known what causes its reddish color. Hypotheses supported by laboratory experiments suppose that the color may be caused by chemical products created from the solar ultraviolet irradiation of ammonium hydrosulfide and the organic compound acetylene, which produces a reddish material.

items.name: name:South_Pole_Aitken_Basin_Detail
items.zh: "它是月球背面一座巨大的撞击陨石坑，直径大约2500公里，深13公里，最大落差（从坑底最深处到最高壁顶处）16

items.name: .1公里，它是太阳系中已知最大的撞击坑之一，也被公认为是月球上最大、最古老和最深的撞击盆地。"
items.application: An immense impact crater on the far side of the Moon. At roughly 2,500 km in diameter and 13 km deep (from floor to highest wall), it is one of the largest known impact craters in the Solar System. It is the largest, oldest, and deepest basin recognized on the Moon.

items.name: name:Copernicus_Detail
items.zh: "它是月球风暴洋东部一座陨石坑，属于保存完好、非常突出的月球环形山之一，周围环绕着巨大明亮的射纹系统，直径96.07公里，深度2

items.name: .846公里。它大约形成于8亿年前，为月球最年轻的大型陨石坑之一。"
items.application: An impact crater located on the eastern side of Oceanus Procellarum. It is one of the most pronounced craters on the Moon and is very well preserved with a prominent ray system. It has a diameter of 96.07 km and a depth of 2.846 km. Formed approximately 800 million years ago, it is one of the youngest large-scale impact craters on the Moon.

items.name: name:Oceanus_Procellarum_Detail
items.zh: "它是月球近月面西侧，形成于31-35亿年前的一座巨大的月海。由于面积最大，它也是月球上唯一被称为"洋"的月海，横跨月球南北中轴线绵延达2500公里以上，其范围约400

items.name: 万平方公里。"
items.application: A vast lunar mare formed approximately 3.1-3.5 billion years ago, located on the western edge of the near side of the Moon. It is the only one of the lunar maria to be called an "Oceanus" (ocean), due to its size, as it stretches more than 2,500 km across its north-south axis and covers roughly 4,000,000 km2.

items.name: name:Amazonia_Detail
items.zh: 它位于南美洲亚马逊盆地的热带雨林，占地550万平方公里，使这片雨林生机盎然的就是亚马逊河。它占世界雨林面积的一半，森林面积的20%，是全球最大及物种最多的热带雨林。
items.en: A moist broadleaf tropical rainforest in the Amazon biome that covers most of the Amazon basin of South America. 5,500,000 square kilometers of this basin are covered by the rainforest. The region represents over half of the planet's remaining rainforests, and comprises the largest and most biodiverse tract of tropical rainforest in the world.

items.name: name:North_Pole_Detail
items.zh: 它与南极地区一起构成了地球的寒带。它主要由一个被广大冰原覆盖的大洋（即北冰洋）和环绕在其周围的一圈无树木的冻土地带所组成。在全球气候变暖的影响下，近年来北极地区的冰盖厚度在不断下降。
items.en: The Arctic and Antarctic regions are the two frigid zones on earth. The Arctic consists of a vast ice-covered ocean (the Arctic Ocean) surrounded by treeless, frozen ground. Global warming is decreasing the thickness of the sea ice in the Arctic region.

items.name: name:privacy_app_protect_open_dialog_msg

items.en: We recommend encryption %s to protect your privacy.

items.name: name:rcs_reboot_tips

items.name: name:rcs_reboot_tips
items.zh: 为了保证增强信息功能正常，手机将在 %s 秒钟后重启。

items.name: name:rcs_reboot_tips

items.en: To ensure the functionality of China Mobile RCS, the phone will reboot in %s seconds.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_5
items.zh: 为了更好地保护您的隐私，我们基于设备标识向您发送广告。具体而言，我们在设备上为每位用户生成唯一的设备标识。设备标识可以被用户随时进行重置。基于设备标识，我们可以将所收集的用户个人信息与该用户的设备标识进行关联，进而通过使用个人信息，为您提供关联度更高的定制化、个性化的广告体验。
items.en: To better protect your privacy, we display ads based on your device ID. Specifically, we generate a unique device ID for each device, and you can choose to reset the device ID at any time. The device ID allows us to associate personal information that we have collected on a specific device so that we can provide you with a more relevant, customized and targeted advertising experience.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_5
items.zh: 为了更好地保护您的隐私，我们及我们的合作方基于设备标识向您发送广告。具体而言，我们在设备上为每位用户生成唯一的设备标识。设备标识可以被用户随时进行重置。基于设备标识，我们可以将所收集的用户个人信息与该用户的设备标识进行关联，进而通过使用个人信息，为您提供关联度更高的定制化、个性化的广告体验。
items.en: To better protect your privacy, we and our partners push ads based on your device ID. Specifically, a unique device ID is generated for each device, and you can choose to reset the device ID at any time. This allows us to associate your personal information with your device ID so that we can provide you with a more relevant, customized, and targeted advertising experience.

items.name: name:ted_warning_verification_code_exp
items.zh: 为了您的财产安全，请勿向他人泄露验证码！
items.en: For the security of your property, do not disclose your verification code to others!

items.name: name:ted_warning_verification_code_open_exp
items.zh: 为了您的财产安全，请勿向他人泄露验证码（系统已禁止第三方应用自动读取验证码）！
items.en: For the security of your property, do not disclose your verification code to others (third party apps are now prohibited by the system to automatically access verification code)!

items.name: name:frp_verify_dialog_message
items.zh: 为了您的手机安全，请连接WLAN或数据网络进行身份验证。
items.en: To protect your phone, please connect to a Wi-Fi or mobile data network to authenticate.

items.name: name:ted_warning_safe
items.zh: 为了您的信息安全，如果短信中有涉及财产的操作，请一定先核实身份。
items.en: Beware of messages that concern your bank accounts or property. Please verify the identity of the contact first.

items.name: name:color_oppo_set_default_sms_mms_toast
items.zh: 为了您的信息安全，已将系统信息设置为默认信息应用。
items.en: The system messaging app has been set as the default message app to ensure that your messages are secure.

items.name: name:phone_download_notification_mobile_net_content2

items.en: To save data usage, we disabled the offline function over a 2G/3G/4G network

items.name: name:phone_download_notification_mobile_net_content2

items.en: For saving data, we disabled the offline function under 2G/3G network

items.name: name:wifi_random_mac_confirm_message

items.en: For the security and privacy of your device, we recommend using a random MAC address.

items.name: name:bt_multi_summary_content_4
