items.en: You can calibrate connected Bluetooth speakers to better sync audio with video.

items.name: name:bt_multi_adjust_tips
items.zh: 为了使手机视频上的音画同步更加准确，你可以校准已经连接的蓝牙设备。
items.en: You can calibrate connected Bluetooth devices to better sync audio with video.

items.name: name:oppo_protocol_26
items.zh: 为了提高产品使用体验，OPPO会在您使用本产品一段时间后，邀请您参与问卷调查。OPPO不会在问卷中收集您的个人数据，但是会通过APP收集您的设备名称、设备版本、设备识别码（IMEI、SN）、操作系统版本、本应用程序版本、地区和语言设置，以便分析您在产品使用过程中的体验。
items.en: To provide better product experience, OPPO will invite you to complete questionnaire surveys after you have used the product for some time. OPPO will not collect your personal data in the questionnaire, but will use this app to collect your device name, device version, device identification number (IMEI, SN), OS version, version of this app, as well as region and language settings to analyze your product use experience.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_8
items.zh: 为了向您展示广告信息，我们会与我们合作的第三方合作伙伴共享您的设备标识及与该设备标识所关联的个人信息（如用户画像标签）。第三方合作伙伴可能基于设备标识来向您推送您可能感兴趣的个性化广告，并衡量分析其广告展示的效果。
items.en: In order to display ads to you, we will share your device ID and personal information associated with the device ID (such as profiles) with our third-party partners. Third-party partners may display targeted ads that you may be interested in based on your device ID and measure the effectiveness of the ads displayed by them.

items.name: name:ted_recognition_will_connect_net_content

items.en: In order to identify unknown numbers (such as harassing and fraudulent calls) online, the Identification of Unknown Numbers function requires a small amount of data usage when in use. Do you accept?

items.name: name:private_policy_text_34
items.zh: 位置信息——当您使用ColorOS提供若干基于位置的程序服务和功能时，我们需收集您的位置信息。例如：当您进行基于位置的搜索、使用基于位置的广告、利用位置优化天气功能或索取地图信息时，您的位置信息可能被发回ColorOS，以便ColorOS向您提供正确的内容。
items.en: Location information - When you are using location-based program services and functions provided by ColorOS, we will need to collect information of your location. For example, when you perform location-based searches, use location-based advertisements, utilize location-based weather functions or request map information, information of your location may be sent back to ColorOS so that ColorOS can provide you with the correct contents.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_3
items.zh: 我们的隐私政策包括了以下几个方面的问题
items.en: Our Privacy Policy covers the following issues:

items.name: name:private_policy_text_64
items.zh: 我们的隐私政策不适用于第三方产品和/或服务。ColorOS的产品和服务中可能含有第三方产品和服务，当您使用第三方产品或接收第三方服务时，他们可能获取您的信息，因此，我们在此提醒您注意阅读第三方的隐私政策。
items.en: Our Privacy Policy shall not apply to the products and/or services of third parties. The ColorOS products and services may contain third party products and services. When you use third party products or utilize third party services, they may obtain your information. Therefore, you are reminded that you should read and understand the privacy policies of third parties.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_60
items.zh: 我们对多项服务进行了多重加密。我们会审查信息收集、存储和处理方面的做法（包括物理性安全措施），以避免各种系统遭到未经授权的访问。
items.en: We have implemented multiple-level encryption for a variety of services. We will examine our practice of information collection, storage, and processing (including physical security measures) to prevent the systems from unauthorized access.

items.name: name:settings_about_watch_user_joinin_info
items.zh: 我们会统计你的功能的使用情况，以提升产品和服务，整个过程将遵循用户体验计划政策。
items.en: We will collect your usage data to improve our products and services. We will comply with the User Experience Program policy during the entire process.

items.name: name:user_experience_summery
items.zh: 我们会统计您对产品各功能项的使用情况，以提升产品和服务，整个过程将遵循隐私政策。您可以在设置—安全与隐私中开启和关闭。
items.en: We will collect the data on how you use each function for the purpose of improving products and services. All data collection is fully compliant with the privacy policy. You can enable or disable this function under Settings - Safety and Privacy.

items.name: name:privacy_user_experience_summery
items.zh: 我们会统计您对产品各项功能的使用情况，以提升产品和服务。整个过程将遵循隐私政策。
items.en: We will collect information about use of various functions of the product to improve the product and services. The collection process will comply with privacy policies.

items.name: name:privacy_user_experience_summery
items.zh: 我们会统计您对产品各项功能的使用情况，以提升产品与服务。整个过程将遵循隐私政策。
items.en: We will collect statistics on your use of various product functions to improve the product and service. The collection process will be in compliance with our privacy policy.

items.name: name:privacy_user_experience_summery
items.zh: 我们会统计您对各项功能的使用情况，以提升产品和服务。整个过程将遵循隐私政策。
items.en: We will collect information about your usage of different functions for products and services improvement purpose. The entire process will comply with the Privacy Policy.

items.name: name:privacy_user_experience_summery_exp_euex
items.zh: 我们会统计您对功能的使用情况，以提升产品和服务。整个过程将遵循用户体验计划政策。
items.en: The User Experience Program collects your usage information to improve products and services. This is subject to the User Experience Program Policy.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_67
items.zh: 我们建议限制行为能力人（具体年龄依您所在地法律规定）在其法定监护人的许可和指导下使用ColorOS产品或服务。
items.en: We recommend that individuals with limited capacity to act on their own (Provisions of the law of your place shall apply with respect to the specific age) to use the ColorOS products or services under the approval and guidance of their legal guardians.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_55
items.zh: 我们将个人信息提供给我们的子公司、关联公司或其他可信赖的企业或个人，以便其代表我们处理个人信息。我们要求上述各方同意按照我们的规定、本隐私权政策以及其他任何适用的保密和安全措施来处理这些个人信息。
items.en: We will provide personal information to our subsidiaries, associated companies, or other trustworthy enterprises or individuals, so that they can act on our behalf to process the personal information. We request the foregoing parties to agree to process such personal information pursuant to our requirements, this Privacy Policy, and applicable encrypting and security measures.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_57
items.zh: 我们可能会基于经营或保护用户的需要，如为了展示我们产品或服务的整体使用趋势，同公众以及合作伙伴合理地分享汇总的非个人信息。
items.en: We may, based on operation needs or user protection, such as for presenting the general trend of use of our products and services, reasonably share with the public or partners summarized non-personal information.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_39
items.zh: 我们可以通过分析ColorOS“用户体验改进计划”获取的统计数据来持续不断地提升产品和服务的操作体验、运行性能、修复问题、改善功能设计等。
items.en: With the statistical data obtained from an analysis of the ColorOS "User Experience Improvement Program", we can continually improve our products and services in terms of user-friendliness, operational performance, problem fixing, and function and design enhancement.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_59
items.zh: 我们努力为ColorOS的用户提供保护，以免我们保存的信息在未经授权的情况下被访问、篡改、披露或破坏。为此，我们特别采取了以下措施：
items.en: We strive to provide protection for users of ColorOS in order to prevent unauthorized access to, tampering or disclosure of, and damage to our stored information. Therefore, we have specially taken the below measures:

items.name: name:private_policy_text_22
items.zh: 我们收集的个人信息将被用于我们的产品和服务开发，尽管一般情况下，我们为此目的仅使用综合信息和统计性信息。
items.en: The personal information that we collect will be used for the development of our products and services, although generally only consolidated and statistical information is used for this purpose.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_21
items.zh: 我们收集的个人信息将被用于向您提供ColorOS的产品和服务、处理您的订单或履行您与ColorOS之间的合同，以确保我们产品和服务的功能和安全、验证您的身份、防止并追究欺诈或其他不当使用的情形。
items.en: The personal information that we collect will be used for providing you with ColorOS products and services, and for processing your orders or fulfilling the agreement between you and ColorOS, in order to ensure the functionality and security of our products and services, verify your identity, and prevent and act against frauds and other instances of improper use.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_23
items.zh: 我们收集的个人信息将被用于与您进行交流，例如，在ColorOS产品或服务更新、发布的第一时间向您发出通知。
items.en: The personal information that we collect may be used to communicate with you. For example, in order to promptly notify you of any ColorOS product or service updates/releases.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_38
items.zh: 我们收集的诸如职业、语言、邮编、区号以及使用ColorOS产品所在的时区等非个人信息，可以帮助我们更好地了解用户行为，改进我们的产品、服务和广告宣传。
items.en: The non-personal information that we collect, such as profession, language, postcode, area code and the time zone where ColorOS is used, can help us better understand user behaviors and improve our products, services and advertisements.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_9
items.zh: 我们收集您的两种信息：个人信息（个人信息是可用于唯一地识别或联系某人的数据）和非个人信息（即不会与任何特定个人直接相关联的数据）。如果我们将非个人信息与个人信息合并在一起，在保持合并的期间内，此类信息将被视为个人信息。
items.en: We collect two types of information from you: personal information (Personal information are unique data that can be used to identify or contact someone) and non-personal information (namely data that are not unique to any particular person). If we consolidate non-personal information with personal information, such information will be deemed as personal information during the period of consolidation.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_24
items.zh: 我们所收集的个人信息将被用于进行产品的个性化设计，并向您提供更为贴身的服务，例如：在我们的服务中进行推荐、展示专为您打造的内容和广告或者用于调研。
items.en: The personal information that we collect may be used for product design customization and personalization services. For example, when recommending and presenting content and advertisement that are specially designed for you in our services, or supporting research efforts.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_40
items.zh: 我们通过使用cookies和其他技术（例如像素标签）收集到的信息，为您带来更好的用户体验，并提高我们的总体服务品质。例如，通过保存您的语言偏好设置，我们可以用您的首选语言显示我们的服务。我们可以通过使用像素标签向用户发送可阅读格式的电子邮件，并告知我们邮件是否被打开。我们可将此等信息用于减少向用户发送电子邮件或者不向用户发送电子邮件。
items.en: The information that we collect by using cookies and other technologies (such as pixel tags) provide you with better user experience and improve our overall service quality. For example, by saving your language preference setting, we can display our services in your preferred language. We can send to users emails in readable formats by using pixel tags, and know whether the emails have been opened. We can use such information to reduce emails to users or stop sending emails to users.

items.name: name:setting_laboratory_summary
items.zh: 我们希望进行一些大胆的尝试，为用户提供更有趣、更新潮的功能和体验，请告诉我们你是否喜欢这个功能！
items.en: We are working to develop cool features you may find useful. Please let us know if you like the feature.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_54
items.zh: 我们因法律调查、诉讼、强制执行或其它法律强制性规定或要求，而同第三方共享这些个人信息。
items.en: We may share personal information with third parties due to legal investigation, litigation, and compulsory execution or other mandatory provisions or requirements of the law.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_61
items.zh: 我们只允许那些为了帮我们处理个人信息而需要知晓这些信息的ColorOS员工、授权代为处理服务公司的人员访问个人信息，而且他们需要履行严格的合同保密义务，如果其未能履行这些义务，就可能会被追究法律责任或被终止其与ColorOS的关系。
items.en: We will only allow those ColorOS employees who need to know such information in order to help us process personal information and those personnel of the companies authorized to handle services on our behalf to access personal information, and they will need to fulfill strict contractual confidentiality obligations. Should they fail to fulfill these obligations, they may be held accountable for legal responsibilities or their relationship with ColorOS may be terminated.

items.name: name:private_policy_text_48
items.zh: 无论您在何时使用我们的服务，我们都力求让您能够访问自己的个人信息。如果这些信息有误，我们会努力通过各种方式让您快速更新信息或删除信息（除非我们出于合法业务或法律方面的原因而必须保留这些信息）。在更新您的个人信息时，我们可能会要求您先验证自己的身份，然后再处理您的请求。
items.en: Whenever you use our services, we seek to allow you to access your own personal information. If there are incorrect information, we will try all means to let you quickly update or delete the information (unless we have to keep such information due to business legality or legal causes). When updating your personal information, we may request you to first have your identity verified before we process your request.

items.name: name:str_ipmsg_introduction
items.zh: 无论是群聊，群发还是单聊，iSMS让您亲历一张列表快捷查找的便利；让您体验免费消息即时送达的畅快。一切只需轻轻点击，即可开启您的专属体验。
items.en: No matter whether it is a group chat, group message or private chat, iSMS offers you a convenient way of communication by quickly browsing one single list. You will enjoy the unique experience of sending free and instant messages just using a few clicks.

items.name: name:root_dialog_txt
items.zh:
系统被 ROOT 后，可能导致手机卡顿、发热，照片、联系人、帐号等隐私信息被第三方软件窃取的风险。

您可以通过以下两种方法修复：
1. 连接 WLAN 网络更新系统；
2. 去 OPPO 售后处理。
items.en:
When the system is rooted, the phone may have hanging or heating issues, and your private information such as photos, contacts, and accounts may be stolen by third-party apps.

You can fix this by:
1. Updating the system via Wi-Fi.
2. Visiting an OPPO after-sales service site for assistance.

2. 去售后处理。
items.en:
When your system is rooted it may cause the phone to lag or heat up, and your private information such as photos, contacts, and accounts to be stolen by third-party apps.

You can fix this by:

2. Visiting an after-sales service site for assistance.

items.name: name:health_ecg_desc
items.zh: 心电图（ECG）英文全称为 ElectroCardioGram, 是利用心电图采集设备记录心脏每一个心动周期所产生电活动变化的曲线图形，能够反应心脏跳动的情况。作为常用的临床检查方法之一，通过心电图可以检查出多种心脏疾病，例如心律异常，室性早搏和房室窦房阻滞等。
items.en: An electrocardiogram (ECG) is a test that checks how your heart is functioning by measuring the electrical activity of the heart during a cardiac cycle. It is one of the most common clinical methods for detecting heart conditions including arrhythmia, ventricular premature beats, and atrioventricular block.

items.name: name:health_heart_rate_standard_description
items.zh: 心率健康状况评估主要的参考指标为静息心率值。健康成年人的静息心率值约为50–95次/分，理想的静息心率值为55–70次/分。通过运动锻炼和保持健康的生活方式可以使静息心率变慢。
items.en: Your resting heart rate can usually tell you how healthy your heart is. The resting heart rate of a healthy adult is somewhere between 50-95 beats per minute. Ideally, it should be somewhere between 55-70 beats per minute. Exercise and a healthy lifestyle can help lower your resting heart rate.

items.name: name:sports_record_heart_beat_max_heart_beat_content
items.zh: 心率区间是通过最大心率的百分比进行划分。最大心率=220-你的年龄，例如25岁的人，最大心率为195。
items.en:
A heart rate zone is a percentage range of your maximum heart rate (MHR).
 MHR = 220 - your age
For example, if you are 25, your MHR is 195.

items.name: name:unhs_description
items.zh: 新生儿听力筛查(Universal Newborn Hearing Screening，UNHS)，是通过耳声发射、自动听性脑干反应和声阻抗等电生理学检测，在新生儿出生后自然睡眠或安静的状态下进行的客观、快速和无创的检查。国内外报道表明，正常新生儿和高危因素新生儿听力损失发病率的差异较大，正常新生儿约为1‰～3‰，高危因素新生儿约为2%～4%。
items.en: Universal newborn hearing screening is a quick and noninvasive hearing loss detection procedure performed on newborns when they are sleeping or at rest. It uses objective testing methods to assess their otoacoustic emissions, automated auditory brainstem response, and acoustical impedance. It has been reported that high-risk infants tend to experience hearing loss more easily than normal infants. 0.1% to 0.3% of normal infants are likely to lose their hearing, whereas for high-risk infants that number is around 2% to 4%.

items.en: Due to circumstances beyond its control, OPPO makes no warranties that all services will function normally or be free from defects at all times. Due to the fact that some countries and regions lack the environment and conditions necessary for this Service, this Service may not be available in these countries and regions. For example, services like online scheduling of mail-in repairs or reservation for shop repairs may not work properly in certain countries and regions. OPPO has the right to change, delete, restrict, block access to or stop providing some or all of its services without notice as it deems proper and reasonable.

items.name: name:bt_multi_summary_content_1
items.zh: 由于蓝牙和 WLAN 在相同频道上发送信号，连接多个设备会增加干扰风险。在只连接 <xliff:g id="ssid">%s</xliff:g> 台设备的情况下，你的蓝牙设备会有最佳的连接状态和最良好的音频音质。
items.en: As Bluetooth and Wi-Fi share the same frequency spectrum, their radio signals may interfere with each other when your phone is connected to multiple Bluetooth devices. For the best connection status and audio quality, your phone should be connected to no more than <xliff:g id="ssid">%s</xliff:g> Bluetooth devices when Wi-Fi is also being used.

items.name: name:power_control_detail
items.zh:
允许唤醒前台：

关闭后，将有效减少应用耗电量，但可能导致该应用无法正常运行，相应通知也可能会有所延迟。


允许完全后台行为：

开启后，不对应用后台行为进行任何限制与优化，可能导致应用耗电量增加。
items.en:
Allow Foreground Activity

You can turn this function off to save battery power.. However, this app may not run properly and app notifications may be delayed. 


Allow All Background Activity

When turned on, no background activity for this app will be restricted. This may consume more battery power.

items.name: name:power_control_detail

允许完全后台行为：

开启后，不对应用后台行为进行任何限制与优化，可能导致应用耗电量增加。
items.en:
Allow Foreground Activity: 

Turning off this function will reduce power consumption. However, the app may not run properly and notifications for this app may be delayed. 


Allow Background Activity: 

If turned on, background activity of this app will not be restricted or optimized, but the app will consume more power.

items.name: name:direction_for_use_second_paragraph
items.zh: 在浏览文章、视频、商品等页面时，用拇指大面积按压屏幕上的文字，呼出 Breeno 识屏。如生成收藏卡片，点击收藏卡片底部的“收藏”按钮，就可以将该页面添加到“自由收藏”，下次可以在桌面最边缘一屏 Breeno 速览中查看，也可以去设置页面中为自由收藏添加桌面图标（设置—Breeno—Breeno 识屏—为自由收藏添加桌面图标）
items.en: When reading articles, watching videos, or viewing online shopping websites on your phone, you can touch and hold any content on the screen to bring up Breeno Touch. If Breeno Touch recognizes the content, it will generate an Add to Favorites card. Simply tap it to add the current page to My Favorites. This page can then be viewed at any time in your Breeno Feed located on the leftmost screen. Alternatively, you can add a My Favorites home screen icon by going to Settings - Breeno - Breeno Touch and tapping the Add a Homescreen Icon for My Favorites option.

items.name: name:direction_for_use_second_paragraph
items.zh: 在浏览文章、视频、商品等页面时，用拇指大面积按压屏幕上的文字，呼出 Breeno 识屏。如生成收藏卡片，点击收藏卡片底部的“收藏”按钮，就可以将该页面添加到“自由收藏”，下次可以在桌面最边缘一屏 Breeno 速览中查看，也可以去设置页面中为自由收藏添加桌面图标（设置—智能便捷—Breeno 识屏—为自由收藏添加桌面图标）
items.en: When reading articles, watching videos, or viewing online shopping websites on your phone, you can touch and hold any content on the screen to bring up Breeno Touch. If Breeno Touch recognizes the content, it will generate an Add to Favorites card. Simply tap it to add the current page to My Favorites. This page can then be viewed at any time in your Breeno Feed located on the leftmost screen. Alternatively, you can add a My Favorites home screen icon by going to Settings - Breeno - Breeno Touch and tapping the Add a Homescreen Icon for My Favorites option.

items.name: name:direction_for_use_second_paragraph
items.zh: 在浏览文章、视频、商品等页面时，用拇指大面积按压屏幕上的文字，呼出智慧识屏。如生成收藏卡片，点击收藏卡片底部的“收藏”按钮，就可以将该页面添加到“自由收藏”，下次可以在桌面最边缘一屏智能助手中查看，也可以去设置页面中为自由收藏添加桌面图标（设置—智能便捷—智慧识屏—为自由收藏添加桌面图标）
items.en: When you are browsing articles, videos, products etc., pressed your thumb against the text on the screen to call up Smart Screen Recognition. If a Favorites card is generated, tap the "Favorites" button at the bottom of the card to add it to My Favorites. To view it, go to the Smart Assistant on the first page of the homescreen, or go to the settings page to add a homescreen icon for My Favorites (Settings-Smart Convenience-Smart Screen Recognition-Add Homescreen Icon for My Favorites)

items.name: name:direction_for_use_second_paragraph

items.name: name:direction_for_use_first_paragraph
items.zh: 在移动互联网时代，我们每天都在各个移动应用之间跳转：在阅读新闻资讯或者在电商平台浏览产品时，中途会跳转出去回复微信或者查询其他信息；在看视频的时候，由于时间有限，会暂时停止观看。很多时候，我们会用到各个应用内的“收藏”功能，方便我们以后继续浏览。但是问题来了，如果多个平台都有收藏，那么二次浏览的时候只能通过对应的平台单独浏览，而且很多时候都必须得注册登录之后才能完成收藏这个动作；这样的方式耗时费力，可能为了找某一条内容而翻遍整个手机。现在我们系统自带的“自由收藏”功能，提供了一个手机上统一的收藏夹，能够支持你在各个应用内把暂时没有读完的页面收藏下来，下次再看。
items.en: In the era of mobile Internet, we use and switch between many mobile applications: when reading news or browsing products on e-commerce platforms, we may switch to WeChat to reply a message or search for information, when watching a video, we may need to pause it due to time constraint. Oftentimes, we need to use the Favorites function in apps to help us continue with the browsing at a later time. But there is a problem. If you have Favorites in different platforms, to view them again, you need to access the corresponding platform individually. Besides, oftentimes account registration and sign-in is required before you can add to Favorites, this is time consuming and it's tedious to find the content you want in your phone. Our system has now a built-in function, My Favorites, where a common folder is provided in the phone for you to store the pages of different apps you have not completed viewing as Favorites for easy access at a later time.

items.name: name:privacy_protect_category_des_main
items.zh: 在应用需要读取以下个人信息时系统将提供空信息，避免真实信息泄露
items.en: When an app tries to read the personal information listed below, the system will provide empty information to avoid real information leakage.

items.name: name:direct_instructions_description
items.zh: 在应用中的文本上保持长按直到底部加载条结束，将提供信息推送和选词编辑功能。已支持地址、美食、影视、快递、航班、车次和淘口令等信息服务。
items.en: Pushing of information, words selection and editing functions will be provided when you touch and hold text in the app until the loading bar at the bottom is complete. Supported information services include addresses, fine dining, movies and TV programs, couriers, flights, train info, and Taobao passphrases.

items.name: name:direct_instructions_description_multi
items.zh: 在应用中的文本上双指长按，将提供信息推送和选词编辑功能。已支持地址、美食、影视、快递、航班、车次和淘口令等信息服务。
items.en: Pushing of information, words selection and editing functions will be provided when you touch and hold text in the app with two fingers. Supported information services include addresses, fine dining, movies and TV programs, couriers, flights, train info, and Taobao passphrases.

items.name: name:location_detail_package_desc_data
items.zh: 在有效期内套餐流量使用完毕，则会停止服务。
items.en: The service will be stopped if the data in the package has been used up in the validity period.

items.name: name:location_detail_package_desc_data
items.zh: 在有效期内套餐流量使用完毕，则会停止流量套餐。
items.en: The data package will be stopped if the data in the package has been used up in the validity period.

items.name: name:display_describe
items.zh: 在月视图、周视图下显示此日历的日程。
items.en: Show events on this calendar in monthly and weekly calendar views.

items.name: name:sight_line_detection_summary_detail
items.zh: 在阅读电子书时，手机将会侦测您的视线，当视线在屏幕上时常亮
items.en: When reading an e-book, your mobile phone will detect your sight and keep the screen on.

items.name: name:air_filp_page_summary_detail
items.zh: 在阅读应用中，手掌在听筒上方3–9cm处左右挥动可左右翻页
items.en: Wave the palm of your hand left or right 3-9 cm above the earpiece to turn pages in the reader app.

items.name: name:air_filp_page_summary_detail
items.zh: 在阅读应用中，手掌在听筒上方3–9cm处左右挥动可左右翻页(翻页方式为滑动时除外）
items.en: In reader applications, you can turn the page by waving your hand to left or right 3-9 cm from the earpiece (unless the page-flip mode is set to Slide).

items.name: name:air_filp_page_summary
items.zh: 在阅读应用中通过手势翻页
items.en: Use gestures to turn pages when you are reading.

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_trible_finger
items.zh: 在支持分屏的应用下，三指上滑即可开启分屏。
items.en: Swipe up with three fingers to enter the Split Screen mode.

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_long_click
items.zh: 在支持分屏的应用下，长按多任务可进入分屏。
items.en: Touch and hold the Recent button in an app that supports Split Screen to open it in the Split Screen mode.

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_long_click
items.zh: 在支持分屏的应用下，长按多任务可开启分屏。
items.en: In an app that supports Split Screen, simply touch and hold the Recent button to split your screen.

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_side_bar
items.zh: 在智能侧边栏中，将支持分屏的应用拖动到侧边栏外可开启分屏。
items.en: Drag an app that supports Split Screen out of Smart Sidebar to open the app in a floating window.

items.name: name:exp_page_title_2679
items.zh: 在智能侧边栏中显示快捷开关
items.en: Display Shortcut Switches in Smart Sidebar

items.name: name:battery_percentage_setting_switch
items.zh: 在状态栏中显示电量百分比
items.en: Show Battery Percentage on Status Bar

items.name: name:shake_clears_memory_summary
items.zh: 在桌面界面摇晃手机清理最近任务
items.en: Shake on the Home screen to delete recent tasks.

items.name: name:double_finger_control_blur_summary
items.zh: 在桌面空白处，可双击切换壁纸模糊效果
items.en: Double tap the blank space on the desktop to switch blur effect for desktop wallpapers

items.name: name:air_sliding_desktop_summary_detail
items.zh: 在桌面时，手掌从听筒上方3–9cm处左右挥动可移动桌面
items.en: When on the homescreen, wave the palm of your hand left or right 3-9 cm above the earpiece to move through homescreen pages.

items.name: name:air_sliding_desktop_summary
items.zh: 在桌面通过隔空手势滑动页面
items.en: On the desktop, use air gestures to slide the pages

items.name: name:home_slide_notification_bar
items.zh: 在桌面下滑可打开通知栏
items.en: Swipe Down on Home Screen to Access

items.name: name:favorite_guide_success
items.zh: 在桌面最左边的负一屏开启“<xliff:g id="name">%1$s</xliff:g>”，并添加“<xliff:g id="name">%2$s</xliff:g>”卡片即可查看收藏的内容
items.en: You can enable "<xliff:g id="name">%1$s</xliff:g>" in the leftmost screen, and add the "<xliff:g id="name">%2$s</xliff:g>" card to navigate My Favorites

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_pull_click
items.zh: 在最近任务中，点击支持分屏的任务卡片右上角进入列表，可在列表中点击“分屏”按钮进入分屏。
items.en: On the Recent screen, tap the upper right corner of a task window and select Split Screen (if available) to open the app in Split Screen.

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_pull_click
items.zh: 在最近任务中，点击支持分屏的应用卡片右上角，在展开的列表中点击“分屏”按钮可开启分屏。
items.en: Tap the Recent button at the bottom of the screen to enter Multitasking Mode, tap the Menu button in the upper right corner of the app, and then tap Split Screen to split your screen. Not all apps support Split Screen.

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_user_guide_tips_pull_click
items.zh: 在最近任务中，下拉支持分屏的任务卡片，可点击“分屏”按钮进入分屏。
items.en: "After pulling down a task card that supports the split-screen function in Recent Tasks, you can tap the "Split-screen" Button to enter split-screen mode."

items.name: name:oppo_setting_split_screen_small_icon_user_guide_tips_pull_click
items.zh: 在最近任务中，下拉支持分屏的任务图标，可点击“分屏”按钮进入分屏。
items.en: After pulling down a task icon that supports the Split Screen function in recent tasks, you can tap the "Split Screen" Button to enter Split Screen mode.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_1
items.zh: 在尊重及保护用户隐私的基础上，我们(和我们的关联公司)及第三方合作伙伴将通过我们的广告平台基于您的偏好及兴趣，在您使用我们的产品及服务过程中向您展示个性化广告信息。本隐私声明旨在帮您了解我们与广告推送相关的个人信息收集和处理实践
items.en: While respecting and protecting your privacy, each time you use our products, we (including our affiliates) and our third-party partners will show targeted ads to you through our advertising platform based on your preferences and interests. This Privacy Statement is designed to explain to you how we collect and process your personal information in connection with advertising.

items.name: name:advertise_and_privacy_policy_1
items.zh: 在尊重及保护用户隐私的基础上，我们及第三方合作伙伴将通过我们的广告平台基于您的偏好及兴趣，在您使用我们的产品过程中向您展示个性化广告信息。本隐私声明旨在帮您了解我们与广告推送相关的个人信息收集和处理实践
items.en: While respecting and protecting your privacy, we and our third-party partners will serve targeted ads to you through our advertising platform based on your preferences and interests during your use of our products. This Privacy Statement is designed to explain to you how we collect and process personal information in connection with advertising.

items.name: name:rcs_detail_introduction_new
items.zh: 增强信息，是传统短彩信的增强功能，支持通过数据或WLAN网络发送文字、图片、语音与视频等消息，并支持多人群聊功能，在中国移动内部被称为“和飞信”。点击查看%1$s、%2$s与%3$s。
items.en: RCS is an instant messaging feature that allows you to use Wi-Fi or the mobile network to send and receive text messages, images, audio, and videos as well as create group chats. China Mobile's RCS product is known as WorkMate. View the %1$s, %2$s, and %3$s.

items.name: name:str_ipmsg_term_warn_activate
items.zh:
这个功能一定要开启iSMS服务才能使用。

iSMS服务让你在任何地方任何时候通过WIFI或其他数据网络与朋友免费聊天或分享内容，很方便。

服务条款
items.en:
To use this feature you will first have to activate iSMS service. 

iSMS is a free and convenient service that enables you to chat and share content with your friends anywhere and anytime via WiFi or other data networks. 

Terms of Service

items.name: name:code_setting_clear_all_dialog_tip
items.zh: 这将彻底清除密码本全部数据
items.en: All data in Passwords will be cleared completely.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_data_confirm_hint
items.zh: 这将彻底清除全部数据，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: This will erase all data, and cannot be undone.

items.zh: 这将彻底清除全部数据，同时关闭“查找手机”，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: This operation will clear all data and turn off "Find My Phone", and it cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_data_hint
items.zh: 这将彻底清除全部数据。

items.en: This will reset all system settings without deleting any data or media files.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_app_data_confirm_hint
items.zh: 这将仅还原系统设置项。
items.en: This will reset system settings only.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_data_confirm_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部内容与设置，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: All content and settings will be erased. This operation cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_data_confirm_findphone_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部内容与设置，同时关闭“查找手机”， 此操作无法撤销。
items.en: This will remove all content and settings and turn off "Find My Phone". This operation cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_data_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部内容与设置。
items.en: All content and settings will be erased.

items.name: name:clear_contacts_data_action
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部手机联系人。
items.en: All contacts in your phone will be erased.

items.name: name:clear_message_data_action
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部手机信息。
items.en: All messages in your phone will be erased.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_app_data_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载程序（仅保留用户保存的数据，例如照片与音乐）。此操作执行后将无法撤销。
items.en: This will remove all app data and uninstallable apps (only data such as pictures and music stored by the user will be retained).This operation cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_app_data_confirm_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载程序，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: All app data and removable apps will be erased. This operation cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_app_data_confirm_findphone_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载程序，但不会删除任何数据或媒体,同时关闭“查找手机”，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: This will erase all app data and removable apps without deleting any data or media. It will also turn off "Find My Phone". This action cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_app_data_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载程序，但不会删除任何数据或媒体。
items.en: This will erase all app data and removable apps without deleting any data or media.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_app_data_confirm_findphone_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载程序，同时关闭“查找手机”，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: This will remove all app data & deletable apps and turn off "Find My Phone". This operation cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_app_data_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载程序。
items.en: All app data and removable apps will be erased.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_app_data_confirm_findphone_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载应用，同时关闭“查找手机”，此操作无法撤销。
items.en: This will erase all app data & deletable apps and turn off "Find My Phone". This action cannot be undone.

items.name: name:oppo_clear_all_app_data_hint
items.zh: 这将抹掉全部应用数据与可卸载应用。
items.en: This will erase all app data and deletable apps.

items.name: name:clear_message_data_action
items.zh: 这将抹掉手机短信与彩信。
items.en: This will erase the SMS and MMS messages on this phone.

items.name: name:clear_contacts_data_action

items.name: name:private_policy_text_50
items.zh: 只要我们能够让您访问和修改信息，而且其不需要过多投入，则我们会免费提供。我们力求对服务进行完善的维护，以保护信息免遭意外或恶意的破坏。因此，当您从我们的服务中删除信息后，我们可能不会立即从在用的服务器中删除这些信息的残留副本，也可能不会从备份系统中删除相应的信息。
items.en: Where it is possible we will allow you to access and modify information, and where the provision to do so does not require substantial investment, we will grant it free of charge. We seek to improve our maintenance of the services to protect the information from being accidentally or maliciously damaged. Therefore, when you delete information from our services, we may not immediately delete the residual copies of such information from the server in use, and may not delete the corresponding information from the backup system.
